\c 6  
\s1 There were big, strong fighting men  
\p
\v 1 \w The|strong="H6440"\w* \w people|strong="H2490"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* earth \w kept|strong="H1961"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w having|strong="H1961"\w* lots \w of|strong="H1323"\w* kids, \w and|strong="H6440"\w* \w those|strong="H5921"\w* kids grew \w up|strong="H5921"\w* \w and|strong="H6440"\w* \w kept|strong="H1961"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w having|strong="H1961"\w* \w more|strong="H7231"\w* kids, \w so|strong="H1961"\w* \w after|strong="H5921"\w* some \w time|strong="H1961"\w* \w there|strong="H1961"\w* \w were|strong="H1961"\w* lots \w of|strong="H1323"\w* \w people|strong="H2490"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* earth. \w And|strong="H6440"\w* some \w people|strong="H2490"\w* \w had|strong="H1961"\w* very pretty \w daughters|strong="H1323"\w*.   
