\p
\v 7 \w And|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* said, “\w These|strong="H6213"\w* people \w keep|strong="H6213"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w doing|strong="H6213"\w* bad \w things|strong="H7431"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w makes|strong="H6213"\w* \w me|strong="H6440"\w* really sad. \w I|strong="H3588"\w*’m \w sorry|strong="H5162"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w made|strong="H6213"\w* \w them|strong="H5921"\w*. \w I|strong="H3588"\w*’m \w sorry|strong="H5162"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w made|strong="H6213"\w* everything \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w earth|strong="H8064"\w*. \w I|strong="H3588"\w* want \w to|strong="H5704"\w* finish \w up|strong="H5921"\w* everything. \w I|strong="H3588"\w* want \w to|strong="H5704"\w* kill \w all|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* people \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w made|strong="H6213"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* want \w to|strong="H5704"\w* kill \w all|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* animals \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w earth|strong="H8064"\w*, \w the|strong="H6440"\w* big animals, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w little|strong="H5704"\w* animals, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w even|strong="H5704"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* animals \w that|strong="H3588"\w* crawl \w around|strong="H5921"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w ground|strong="H6440"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* want \w to|strong="H5704"\w* kill \w all|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w birds|strong="H5775"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* fly \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w sky|strong="H8064"\w*.”   
\p
\v 8 \w But|strong="H5146"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w looked|strong="H5869"\w* \w at|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* man called \w Noah|strong="H5146"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w Noah|strong="H5146"\w* \w made|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* happy.   
\s1 The story about Noah  
\p
\v 9 \w This|strong="H1961"\w* \w is|strong="H6662"\w* \w the|strong="H1961"\w* story \w about|strong="H1961"\w* \w Noah|strong="H5146"\w* \w and|strong="H1980"\w* \w his|strong="H1961"\w* family. \w Noah|strong="H5146"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* good \w man|strong="H6662"\w*. \w He|strong="H1980"\w* didn’t do anything wrong. \w He|strong="H1980"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* God’s friend, \w and|strong="H1980"\w* \w he|strong="H1980"\w* \w spent|strong="H1980"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* lot \w of|strong="H8435"\w* \w time|strong="H1961"\w* \w with|strong="H1980"\w* God.\x * \xo 6:9 \xt 2 Peter 2:5\x*  
\v 10 \w He|strong="H5146"\w* \w had|strong="H3205"\w* 3 \w sons|strong="H1121"\w*. Their names \w were|strong="H1121"\w* \w Shem|strong="H8035"\w*, \w Ham|strong="H2526"\w*, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* Jafeth.   
\p
\v 11-12 Everyone on the earth kept on doing bad things. They were doing wrong to each other, and fighting and hurting each other. God looked down and saw all the bad things that were going on. The people were always doing things that were really bad.   
\p
\v 13 \w So|strong="H3588"\w* God said \w to|strong="H6440"\w* \w Noah|strong="H5146"\w*, “\w Look|strong="H2005"\w*, \w everyone|strong="H3605"\w* \w is|strong="H3605"\w* doing bad \w things|strong="H3605"\w* \w and|strong="H6440"\w* hurting \w each|strong="H3605"\w* \w other|strong="H3605"\w*. \w I|strong="H3588"\w*’m \w going|strong="H2005"\w* \w to|strong="H6440"\w* \w kill|strong="H7843"\w* \w everyone|strong="H3605"\w*, \w and|strong="H6440"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H1320"\w* finish \w up|strong="H3605"\w* \w everything|strong="H3605"\w* \w on|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* earth.”   
\s1 God told Noah to build a big boat  
\p
