\c 7  
\s1 God told Noah to get ready for a flood  
\p
\v 1 \w After|strong="H3588"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w*, \w God|strong="H3068"\w* said \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w Noah|strong="H5146"\w*, “\w You|strong="H3588"\w* \w are|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w only|strong="H3588"\w* \w man|strong="H6662"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* lives \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w right|strong="H6662"\w* \w way|strong="H2088"\w*. Get \w your|strong="H3068"\w* \w family|strong="H1004"\w* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w take|strong="H7200"\w* \w them|strong="H6440"\w* \w into|strong="H7200"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* big boat.  
\v 2 \w You|strong="H3605"\w* \w have|strong="H3605"\w* \w to|strong="H4480"\w* \w take|strong="H3947"\w* \w every|strong="H3605"\w* sort \w of|strong="H4480"\w* animal \w with|strong="H8147"\w* \w you|strong="H3605"\w* \w into|strong="H3947"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* big boat. \w You|strong="H3605"\w* know \w the|strong="H3605"\w* sorts \w of|strong="H4480"\w* animals \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w are|strong="H4480"\w* right \w for|strong="H3605"\w* \w you|strong="H3605"\w* \w to|strong="H4480"\w* \w give|strong="H3947"\w* \w to|strong="H4480"\w* \w me|strong="H4480"\w*? Well, \w get|strong="H3947"\w* 7 males \w and|strong="H8147"\w* 7 females \w from|strong="H4480"\w* \w each|strong="H3605"\w* \w of|strong="H4480"\w* \w those|strong="H3605"\w* sorts \w of|strong="H4480"\w* animals. \w And|strong="H8147"\w* \w get|strong="H3947"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w other|strong="H8147"\w* animals \w too|strong="H4480"\w*, \w the|strong="H3605"\w* animals \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w are|strong="H4480"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* right \w to|strong="H4480"\w* \w give|strong="H3947"\w* \w to|strong="H4480"\w* \w me|strong="H4480"\w*. \w Get|strong="H3947"\w* \w one|strong="H3605"\w* male \w and|strong="H8147"\w* \w one|strong="H3605"\w* \w female|strong="H8147"\w* \w from|strong="H4480"\w* \w each|strong="H3605"\w* \w of|strong="H4480"\w* \w those|strong="H3605"\w* sorts \w of|strong="H4480"\w* animals. \w They|strong="H3808"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w have|strong="H3605"\w* \w to|strong="H4480"\w* go \w on|strong="H3605"\w* \w to|strong="H4480"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* big boat.  
\v 3 \w And|strong="H8064"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w birds|strong="H5775"\w* \w too|strong="H1571"\w*. \w They|strong="H5921"\w* \w have|strong="H1571"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* go \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* big boat. Get 7 \w males|strong="H2145"\w* \w and|strong="H8064"\w* 7 females \w from|strong="H6440"\w* \w each|strong="H3605"\w* sort \w of|strong="H6440"\w* \w bird|strong="H5775"\w*. \w That|strong="H3605"\w*’s how \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w can|strong="H2145"\w* \w keep|strong="H2421"\w* \w those|strong="H3605"\w* \w birds|strong="H5775"\w* \w and|strong="H8064"\w* \w animals|strong="H2421"\w* \w alive|strong="H2421"\w*, \w so|strong="H1571"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w there|strong="H6440"\w* \w will|strong="H1571"\w* \w always|strong="H3605"\w* \w be|strong="H1571"\w* \w birds|strong="H5775"\w* \w and|strong="H8064"\w* \w animals|strong="H2421"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w earth|strong="H8064"\w*.   
\p
\v 4 \w You|strong="H3588"\w* see, \w I|strong="H3588"\w*’m going \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w send|strong="H4305"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* big \w rain|strong="H4305"\w*. \w That|strong="H3588"\w* \w rain|strong="H4305"\w* \w will|strong="H5750"\w* \w come|strong="H5750"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* 7 \w days|strong="H3117"\w* \w time|strong="H3117"\w*. \w Then|strong="H6213"\w* \w it|strong="H5921"\w* \w will|strong="H5750"\w* \w keep|strong="H6213"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* raining \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w time|strong="H3117"\w* \w for|strong="H3588"\w* 40 \w days|strong="H3117"\w*. \w The|strong="H3605"\w* \w flood|strong="H5750"\w* water \w will|strong="H5750"\w* \w come|strong="H5750"\w* \w up|strong="H5921"\w* \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \w wash|strong="H4229"\w* \w away|strong="H3605"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w things|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w have|strong="H3117"\w* \w made|strong="H6213"\w*.”   
\p
\v 5 \w So|strong="H6213"\w* \w Noah|strong="H5146"\w* \w did|strong="H6213"\w* \w everything|strong="H3605"\w* \w just|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w way|strong="H3605"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w told|strong="H6680"\w* \w him|strong="H6213"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w*.   
\s1 The flood water came  
\p
\v 6-7 Noah was 600 years old at the time that he went into the big boat to be safe from the flood. Noah, and his wife, and his 3 sons, and their wives too, they all went into the big boat.  
\v 8-9 And \w a|strong="H3068"\w* big mob of animals came to Noah, and he took them into the boat too, just like God told him to. There were all sorts of animals. There were animals that were the right sort to give to God, and animals that were not the right sort to give to God. And there were birds and even animals that crawl around on the ground. And there were males and females of each sort of animal, and they went in 2 at \w a|strong="H3068"\w* time. They all came together on that big boat, just like God wanted them to. \fig Males and females of each sort of animal went on to the boat|src="1db NoahsArk.tif" size="col" ref="7:8-9" \fig*   
\p
\v 10 \w Then|strong="H1961"\w*, 7 \w days|strong="H3117"\w* \w later|strong="H1961"\w*, \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w flood|strong="H3999"\w* \w water|strong="H4325"\w* \w came|strong="H1961"\w*, just \w like|strong="H1961"\w* God said.  
\v 11-16 Noah was 600 years old at the time that the flood water came. It came on the 17th day of the 2nd month of that year.  
\p Noah, and his wife, and his sons, and their wives too, they all went into the big boat. The names of Noah’s sons were Shem, and Ham, and Jafeth, and they each had \w a|strong="H3068"\w* wife. They all went into the boat with all the animals. There were wild animals, and animals that are not wild, and animals that crawl around on the ground. And all the birds were there too. There were males and females of every bird and animal on that big boat. All of the different sorts of animals went into that big boat with Noah. They went in 2 at \w a|strong="H3068"\w* time, just like God told Noah. And after the last animal went into the boat with Noah and his family, God shut the door.  
\p Then, on that same day, the rain came out of the sky. It rained really hard all the time. It was like God opened up \w a|strong="H3068"\w* big window in the sky, and rain poured down. And water came up from springs, and from everywhere under the ground too. It kept on raining all the time for 40 days.  
\v 17 \w The|strong="H5921"\w* \w flood|strong="H3999"\w* \w water|strong="H4325"\w* \w kept|strong="H1961"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* getting \w higher|strong="H7311"\w* \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \w higher|strong="H7311"\w* \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w all|strong="H3117"\w* \w those|strong="H5921"\w* 40 \w days|strong="H3117"\w*, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* big boat \w started|strong="H1961"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* float \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w water|strong="H4325"\w*.  
\v 18 \w The|strong="H6440"\w* \w water|strong="H4325"\w* got deeper \w and|strong="H3212"\w* deeper, \w but|strong="H4325"\w* \w that|strong="H4325"\w* boat \w was|strong="H4325"\w* \w all|strong="H3212"\w* right, \w it|strong="H5921"\w* \w floated|strong="H5921"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w top|strong="H5921"\w* \w of|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w water|strong="H4325"\w*, \w high|strong="H7235"\w* \w above|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w ground|strong="H6440"\w*.   
\p
\v 19 \w The|strong="H3605"\w* \w water|strong="H4325"\w* got \w so|strong="H3966"\w* deep \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w it|strong="H5921"\w* \w covered|strong="H3680"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* big \w mountains|strong="H2022"\w* \w everywhere|strong="H3605"\w*.  
\v 20 \w It|strong="H3680"\w* \w covered|strong="H3680"\w* \w the|strong="H3680"\w* tops \w of|strong="H2022"\w* those \w mountains|strong="H2022"\w* \w with|strong="H3680"\w* \w about|strong="H2022"\w* 7 metres \w of|strong="H2022"\w* \w water|strong="H4325"\w*.  
