\p
\v 18-19 So Noah, and his wife, and his sons, and their wives, they all came out of the big boat. And all the animals and all the birds came out of the big boat too. They came out in groups. Each sort of animal was in its family group.   
\s1 Noah said thank you to God  
\p
\v 20 \w Then|strong="H3947"\w* \w Noah|strong="H5146"\w* piled \w up|strong="H5927"\w* stones \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w make|strong="H3947"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* special table \w with|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* flat top, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* \w got|strong="H3947"\w* \w one|strong="H3605"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w each|strong="H3605"\w* sort \w of|strong="H3068"\w* animal \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w bird|strong="H5775"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w are|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w right|strong="H3068"\w* sorts \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w give|strong="H3947"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* killed \w them|strong="H3947"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* \w put|strong="H5927"\w* \w them|strong="H3947"\w* \w on|strong="H3068"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* special table, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* burned \w them|strong="H3947"\w* \w there|strong="H5927"\w*. \w He|strong="H3068"\w* \w did|strong="H3068"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w give|strong="H3947"\w* \w them|strong="H3947"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w*, \w to|strong="H3068"\w* say \em thank you\em* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w*. \fig Noah killed animals and burned them to say thank you to God|src="01008020 210 - Genesis 8 20 - Noah built and alter unto the Lord.tif" size="col" ref="8:20" \fig*   
\p
\v 21-22 God smelled the meat cooking on that stone table, and he was happy. Then God said to himself, “People always just want to do bad things. They do that all their lives, from when they are little kids, right up until the time they die. But I will never again punish them the same way that I did this time. I will never again finish up everything that breathes air, and I will never again curse the earth. While the earth is still here, the seasons will stay the same. There will always be day and night, and every year there will be \w a|strong="H3068"\w* hot time and \w a|strong="H3068"\w* cold time, \w a|strong="H3068"\w* wet season and \w a|strong="H3068"\w* dry season. There will always be \w a|strong="H3068"\w* right time to plant seeds for food, and \w a|strong="H3068"\w* right time to get the food from those plants.”   
\c 9  
\s1 God promised not to cover the earth with water again  
\p
\v 1 God \w was|strong="H1121"\w* good \w to|strong="H1121"\w* \w Noah|strong="H5146"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w his|strong="H1288"\w* \w sons|strong="H1121"\w*. God said \w to|strong="H1121"\w* \w them|strong="H1121"\w*, “\w I|strong="H1121"\w* want \w you|strong="H1288"\w* \w to|strong="H1121"\w* \w have|strong="H1121"\w* lots \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w kids|strong="H1121"\w*, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w fill|strong="H4390"\w* \w the|strong="H1288"\w* earth \w with|strong="H4390"\w* \w people|strong="H1121"\w*.\x * \xo 9:1 \xt Genesis 1:28\x*  
\v 2 \w I|strong="H5414"\w*’m \w making|strong="H5414"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* boss \w over|strong="H5921"\w* \w everything|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w lives|strong="H2416"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* ground, \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w animals|strong="H2416"\w* \w and|strong="H8064"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w birds|strong="H5775"\w*, \w and|strong="H8064"\w* \w I|strong="H5414"\w*’m \w making|strong="H5414"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* boss \w over|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w fish|strong="H1709"\w* \w and|strong="H8064"\w* \w everything|strong="H3605"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w sea|strong="H3220"\w* \w too|strong="H5921"\w*. \w They|strong="H5921"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* frightened \w of|strong="H3027"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w*.   
\p
\v 3 \w I|strong="H5414"\w* \w gave|strong="H5414"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* bush tucker \w to|strong="H1961"\w* eat, \w and|strong="H2416"\w* \w now|strong="H1961"\w* \w I|strong="H5414"\w*’m \w giving|strong="H5414"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* meat \w to|strong="H1961"\w* eat \w too|strong="H1961"\w*. \w You|strong="H5414"\w* can eat \w anything|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* moves.  
\v 4 \w But|strong="H3808"\w* \w I|strong="H5315"\w*’m telling \w you|strong="H3808"\w* this about \w blood|strong="H1818"\w*. \w Blood|strong="H1818"\w* \w is|strong="H5315"\w* important. \w It|strong="H3808"\w* keeps \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w body|strong="H1320"\w* \w alive|strong="H5315"\w*. \w So|strong="H3808"\w* don’t eat \w any|strong="H5315"\w* \w blood|strong="H1818"\w*. \w You|strong="H3808"\w* \w have|strong="H3808"\w* \w to|strong="H5315"\w* drain \w the|strong="H3808"\w* \w blood|strong="H1818"\w* \w out|strong="H3808"\w* \w of|strong="H1818"\w* \w the|strong="H3808"\w* animal \w before|strong="H3808"\w* \w you|strong="H3808"\w* eat \w it|strong="H3808"\w*. Don’t eat \w any|strong="H5315"\w* \w meat|strong="H1320"\w* \w that|strong="H5315"\w* still \w has|strong="H5315"\w* \w the|strong="H3808"\w* \w blood|strong="H1818"\w* \w in|strong="H1320"\w* \w it|strong="H3808"\w*.\x * \xo 9:4 \xt Leviticus 7:26-27; 17:10-14; 19:26; Deuteronomy 12:16, 23; 15:23\x*  
\v 5 \w And|strong="H3027"\w* \w I|strong="H5315"\w* \w will|strong="H5315"\w* punish \w anyone|strong="H3605"\w* \w and|strong="H3027"\w* \w anything|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* kills \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w person|strong="H5315"\w* \w dead|strong="H5315"\w*. If an \w animal|strong="H2416"\w* kills somebody, \w it|strong="H3605"\w* \w has|strong="H3027"\w* \w to|strong="H3027"\w* die. \w And|strong="H3027"\w* \w it|strong="H3605"\w* \w is|strong="H5315"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* same \w for|strong="H3027"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w person|strong="H5315"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* kills \w another|strong="H1818"\w* \w person|strong="H5315"\w*, \w that|strong="H3605"\w* murderer \w has|strong="H3027"\w* \w to|strong="H3027"\w* die.  
\v 6 \w You|strong="H3588"\w* see, \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w made|strong="H6213"\w* \w people|strong="H1818"\w* \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w be|strong="H1818"\w* \w like|strong="H8210"\w* myself, \w so|strong="H6213"\w* \w they|strong="H3588"\w* \w are|strong="H6213"\w* important. \w So|strong="H6213"\w* \w if|strong="H3588"\w* somebody kills \w another|strong="H1818"\w* \w person|strong="H1818"\w* dead, \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w have|strong="H3588"\w* \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w kill|strong="H8210"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* murderer dead.\x * \xo 9:6 \xt Genesis 1:26; Exodus 20:13; 21:12\x*   
\p
\v 7 But I want \w you|strong="H6509"\w* mob \w to|strong="H7235"\w* have lots \w of|strong="H7235"\w* kids, \w so|strong="H7235"\w* that there will be lots \w of|strong="H7235"\w* people everywhere \w on|strong="H7235"\w* \w the|strong="H7235"\w* earth.”\x * \xo 9:7 \xt Genesis 1:28\x*   
\p
