\v 13 \w So|strong="H4616"\w* listen. \w You|strong="H5315"\w* have \w to|strong="H4616"\w* \w tell|strong="H4994"\w* everyone \w that|strong="H5315"\w* \w you|strong="H5315"\w* \w are|strong="H5315"\w* \w my|strong="H2421"\w* sister. \w Then|strong="H4616"\w* \w they|strong="H5315"\w* \w will|strong="H5315"\w* \w be|strong="H5315"\w* \w good|strong="H3190"\w* \w to|strong="H4616"\w* \w me|strong="H4994"\w*, \w and|strong="H5315"\w* \w they|strong="H5315"\w* \w will|strong="H5315"\w* \w not|strong="H5315"\w* kill \w me|strong="H4994"\w*.”\x * \xo 12:13 \xt Genesis 20:2; 26:7\x*   
\p
\v 14 \w And|strong="H4714"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w*’s \w what|strong="H7200"\w* \w happened|strong="H1961"\w*. \w They|strong="H3588"\w* got \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w Egypt|strong="H4714"\w*, \w and|strong="H4714"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* \w people|strong="H7200"\w* \w there|strong="H1961"\w* \w looked|strong="H7200"\w* \w at|strong="H7200"\w* Sarai, \w and|strong="H4714"\w* \w they|strong="H3588"\w* \w saw|strong="H7200"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w she|strong="H1931"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w really|strong="H3966"\w* \w beautiful|strong="H3303"\w*.  
\v 15 Some \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w them|strong="H7200"\w* worked \w for|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* big boss \w of|strong="H1004"\w* Egypt, \w and|strong="H1004"\w* \w they|strong="H7200"\w* told \w him|strong="H7200"\w*, “Sarai \w is|strong="H1004"\w* really beautiful.” \w So|strong="H3947"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* big boss \w took|strong="H3947"\w* \w her|strong="H3947"\w* \w to|strong="H1004"\w* live \w in|strong="H1004"\w* \w his|strong="H3947"\w* \w house|strong="H1004"\w*.  
\v 16 \w That|strong="H5650"\w* boss \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w very|strong="H3190"\w* \w good|strong="H3190"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* Abram, \w because|strong="H5668"\w* \w he|strong="H1241"\w* thought \w that|strong="H5650"\w* Abram \w was|strong="H1961"\w* Sarai’s brother. \w He|strong="H1241"\w* \w gave|strong="H1961"\w* Abram \w sheep|strong="H6629"\w*, \w and|strong="H5650"\w* goats, \w and|strong="H5650"\w* \w cows|strong="H1241"\w*, \w and|strong="H5650"\w* \w bulls|strong="H1241"\w*, \w and|strong="H5650"\w* \w donkeys|strong="H2543"\w*, \w and|strong="H5650"\w* \w camels|strong="H1581"\w*, \w as|strong="H1961"\w* \w well|strong="H3190"\w* \w as|strong="H1961"\w* \w men|strong="H5650"\w* \w and|strong="H5650"\w* \w women|strong="H8198"\w* \w that|strong="H5650"\w* \w had|strong="H1961"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* work \w for|strong="H5650"\w* Abram.   
\p
\v 17 \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w was|strong="H3068"\w* not happy, \w because|strong="H5921"\w* \w Sarai|strong="H8297"\w* \w was|strong="H3068"\w* living \w with|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* big boss \w of|strong="H1004"\w* Egypt, \w so|strong="H1697"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w made|strong="H3068"\w* \w him|strong="H5921"\w* really sick, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w made|strong="H3068"\w* everyone \w that|strong="H3068"\w* lived \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w his|strong="H3068"\w* \w house|strong="H1004"\w* really sick \w too|strong="H1697"\w*.  
\v 18-19 Then that big boss found out that Sarai was already Abram’s wife, and he got really wild. He sent somebody to get Abram, and he said to Abram, “You did \w a|strong="H3068"\w* really bad thing to me. You tricked me. You didn’t tell me that Sarai is your wife. You said, ‘She is my sister,’ and you let me marry her. Now, here is your wife. Take her back, and then get out of my country.”  
\v 20 \w Then|strong="H7971"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* big boss \w told|strong="H6680"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* soldiers, “\w Get|strong="H7971"\w* Abram, \w and|strong="H7971"\w* Sarai, \w and|strong="H7971"\w* \w everything|strong="H3605"\w* \w they|strong="H5921"\w* own, \w and|strong="H7971"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w their|strong="H3605"\w* workers, \w and|strong="H7971"\w* \w send|strong="H7971"\w* \w them|strong="H5921"\w* \w out|strong="H7971"\w* \w of|strong="H5921"\w* Egypt. \w Send|strong="H7971"\w* \w them|strong="H5921"\w* \w away|strong="H7971"\w*, \w and|strong="H7971"\w* \w do|strong="H6680"\w* \w it|strong="H5921"\w* right \w now|strong="H5921"\w*.” \w So|strong="H7971"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* soldiers did \w that|strong="H3605"\w*. \w They|strong="H5921"\w* \w sent|strong="H7971"\w* Abram \w and|strong="H7971"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* mob \w away|strong="H7971"\w* \w from|strong="H5921"\w* Egypt.   
\c 13  
\s1 Abram and his nephew Lot split up  
\p
\v 1 \w So|strong="H5927"\w* Abram, Sarai, \w and|strong="H4714"\w* \w Lot|strong="H3876"\w* \w left|strong="H5927"\w* \w Egypt|strong="H4714"\w* \w and|strong="H4714"\w* \w went|strong="H5927"\w* \w back|strong="H5927"\w* \w to|strong="H5927"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* dry desert \w country|strong="H5045"\w*. \w They|strong="H1931"\w* \w took|strong="H5927"\w* \w everything|strong="H3605"\w* \w they|strong="H1931"\w* owned, \w and|strong="H4714"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w their|strong="H3605"\w* workers.  
\v 2 Abram \w was|strong="H3966"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w very|strong="H3966"\w* \w rich|strong="H3513"\w* man. \w He|strong="H3701"\w* \w had|strong="H4735"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* lot \w of|strong="H4735"\w* \w silver|strong="H3701"\w* \w and|strong="H3701"\w* \w gold|strong="H2091"\w*, \w and|strong="H3701"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* big mob \w of|strong="H4735"\w* animals.   
\p
\v 3 \w They|strong="H8033"\w* \w were|strong="H1961"\w* \w in|strong="H3212"\w* \w that|strong="H5704"\w* dry desert \w country|strong="H5045"\w* \w for|strong="H5704"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w while|strong="H5704"\w*, \w then|strong="H1961"\w* \w they|strong="H8033"\w* \w went|strong="H3212"\w* north \w from|strong="H5704"\w* \w place|strong="H4725"\w* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w place|strong="H4725"\w* \w until|strong="H5704"\w* \w they|strong="H8033"\w* got \w back|strong="H3212"\w* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w the|strong="H5704"\w* town \w called|strong="H8033"\w* \w Bethel|strong="H1008"\w*. \w They|strong="H8033"\w* camped \w in|strong="H3212"\w* \w the|strong="H5704"\w* same \w place|strong="H4725"\w* \w that|strong="H5704"\w* \w they|strong="H8033"\w* camped \w at|strong="H1961"\w* \w before|strong="H5704"\w*. \w It|strong="H8033"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w between|strong="H5704"\w* \w Bethel|strong="H1008"\w* \w and|strong="H3212"\w* \w the|strong="H5704"\w* town \w called|strong="H8033"\w* Ayi.  
