\c 20  
\s1 Abraham tried to trick a big boss called Abimelek  
\p
\v 1 \w At|strong="H3427"\w* one time, Abraham \w moved|strong="H5265"\w* \w his|strong="H3427"\w* camp \w south|strong="H5045"\w* \w to|strong="H8033"\w* \w the|strong="H8033"\w* \w Negev|strong="H5045"\w* desert, \w and|strong="H8033"\w* \w he|strong="H8033"\w* \w lived|strong="H3427"\w* \w between|strong="H3427"\w* \w the|strong="H8033"\w* 2 towns \w called|strong="H8033"\w* \w Kadesh|strong="H6946"\w* \w and|strong="H8033"\w* \w Shur|strong="H7793"\w*. \w Then|strong="H5265"\w* later, \w he|strong="H8033"\w* \w moved|strong="H5265"\w* \w his|strong="H3427"\w* camp \w to|strong="H8033"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* town \w called|strong="H8033"\w* \w Gerar|strong="H1642"\w*.  
