\v 28 Then Abraham also picked out 7 young female \w sheep|strong="H6629"\w* from \w his|strong="H5324"\w* animals, \w and|strong="H6629"\w* he put them \w to|strong="H5324"\w* \w one|strong="H5324"\w* side.  
\v 29 Abimelek \w asked|strong="H4100"\w* him, “\w Why|strong="H4100"\w* \w did|strong="H4100"\w* \w you|strong="H4100"\w* put \w these|strong="H2007"\w* 7 sheep \w to|strong="H5324"\w* \w one|strong="H5324"\w* \w side|strong="H2007"\w*? \w What|strong="H4100"\w* \w do|strong="H4100"\w* \w you|strong="H4100"\w* mean \w by|strong="H5324"\w* \w that|strong="H5324"\w*?”   
\p
