\p
\v 21 While Rebekah \w was|strong="H3068"\w* getting \w the|strong="H3068"\w* water, Abraham’s \w worker|strong="H2790"\w* \w kept|strong="H2790"\w* \w on|strong="H1870"\w* looking \w at|strong="H3068"\w* \w her|strong="H3045"\w*, \w but|strong="H3808"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* didn’t say \w anything|strong="H3808"\w*. \w He|strong="H3068"\w* waited \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w see|strong="H3045"\w* if \w she|strong="H3808"\w* \w was|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* woman \w that|strong="H3045"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* picked \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* Isaac’s wife.   
\p
\v 22 \w After|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w camels|strong="H1581"\w* \w finished|strong="H3615"\w* \w drinking|strong="H8354"\w*, \w Abraham|strong="H3947"\w*’s worker \w got|strong="H3947"\w* \w some|strong="H3027"\w* \w of|strong="H3027"\w* \w Abraham|strong="H3947"\w*’s presents \w out|strong="H3947"\w*, \w and|strong="H3027"\w* \w he|strong="H3027"\w* \w gave|strong="H3947"\w* Rebekah \w some|strong="H3027"\w* jewellery. \w He|strong="H3027"\w* \w gave|strong="H3947"\w* \w her|strong="H3947"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w gold|strong="H2091"\w* nose \w ring|strong="H5141"\w* \w and|strong="H3027"\w* 2 heavy \w gold|strong="H2091"\w* \w bracelets|strong="H6781"\w* \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w her|strong="H3947"\w* \w arms|strong="H3027"\w*. \w That|strong="H3027"\w* nose \w ring|strong="H5141"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w made|strong="H1961"\w* \w out|strong="H3947"\w* \w of|strong="H3027"\w* 6 grams \w of|strong="H3027"\w* \w gold|strong="H2091"\w*, \w and|strong="H3027"\w* \w those|strong="H5921"\w* \w bracelets|strong="H6781"\w* \w were|strong="H1961"\w* \w made|strong="H1961"\w* \w out|strong="H3947"\w* \w of|strong="H3027"\w* 120 grams \w of|strong="H3027"\w* \w gold|strong="H2091"\w* \w each|strong="H3947"\w*.  
\v 23 \w Then|strong="H3426"\w* \w the|strong="H5046"\w* worker said \w to|strong="H1004"\w* Rebekah, “\w Please|strong="H4994"\w* \w tell|strong="H5046"\w* \w me|strong="H4994"\w*, \w who|strong="H4310"\w* \w is|strong="H3426"\w* \w your|strong="H4994"\w* father?” \w Then|strong="H3426"\w* \w he|strong="H1004"\w* said, “\w Me|strong="H4994"\w* \w and|strong="H1004"\w* \w my|strong="H5046"\w* men, \w we|strong="H3068"\w* want \w to|strong="H1004"\w* \w stay|strong="H3885"\w* \w here|strong="H4725"\w* \w in|strong="H1004"\w* \w this|strong="H5046"\w* town tonight. \w Is|strong="H3426"\w* \w there|strong="H3426"\w* enough \w room|strong="H1004"\w* \w for|strong="H1004"\w* \w us|strong="H4994"\w* \w to|strong="H1004"\w* \w stay|strong="H3885"\w* \w at|strong="H1004"\w* \w your|strong="H4994"\w* father’s \w house|strong="H1004"\w*?”   
\p
\v 24 Rebekah said \w to|strong="H3205"\w* \w the|strong="H3205"\w* worker, “My \w father|strong="H3205"\w*’s name \w is|strong="H1121"\w* \w Bethuel|strong="H1328"\w*. \w His|strong="H3205"\w* mother’s name \w is|strong="H1121"\w* \w Milcah|strong="H4435"\w*, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w his|strong="H3205"\w* \w father|strong="H3205"\w*’s name \w is|strong="H1121"\w* \w Nahor|strong="H5152"\w*.”  
\v 25 \w Then|strong="H1571"\w* Rebekah said, “We \w have|strong="H1571"\w* \w plenty|strong="H7227"\w* \w of|strong="H4725"\w* \w food|strong="H4554"\w* \w for|strong="H4725"\w* \w your|strong="H1571"\w* camels, \w and|strong="H4725"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w have|strong="H1571"\w* \w plenty|strong="H7227"\w* \w of|strong="H4725"\w* dry grass \w for|strong="H4725"\w* them \w to|strong="H5973"\w* \w sleep|strong="H3885"\w* \w on|strong="H4725"\w*. \w And|strong="H4725"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w have|strong="H1571"\w* \w plenty|strong="H7227"\w* \w of|strong="H4725"\w* \w room|strong="H4725"\w* \w for|strong="H4725"\w* \w you|strong="H5973"\w* \w and|strong="H4725"\w* \w your|strong="H1571"\w* \w men|strong="H7227"\w* \w to|strong="H5973"\w* \w stay|strong="H3885"\w* \w with|strong="H5973"\w* us \w tonight|strong="H1571"\w*.”   
\p
\v 26 \w Then|strong="H3068"\w* Abraham’s worker knew \w that|strong="H3068"\w* Rebekah \w was|strong="H3068"\w* Abraham’s relative, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* knew \w that|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* picked her \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w be|strong="H3068"\w* Isaac’s wife. So \w he|strong="H3068"\w* got \w down|strong="H7812"\w* \w on|strong="H3068"\w* \w his|strong="H3068"\w* knees \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w put|strong="H3068"\w* \w his|strong="H3068"\w* face near \w the|strong="H3068"\w* ground, \w to|strong="H3068"\w* thank \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* show \w him|strong="H3068"\w* respect.  
\v 27 \w He|strong="H3068"\w* said, “\w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w*, \w you|strong="H5973"\w* \w are|strong="H3068"\w* really great. \w You|strong="H5973"\w* \w are|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w my|strong="H3068"\w* boss Abraham. \w You|strong="H5973"\w* keep \w on|strong="H1870"\w* \w being|strong="H1004"\w* very \w good|strong="H2617"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w him|strong="H5973"\w*, just \w like|strong="H5973"\w* \w you|strong="H5973"\w* \w promised|strong="H3068"\w* \w him|strong="H5973"\w*. We \w can|strong="H3808"\w* always trust \w you|strong="H5973"\w*. \w You|strong="H5973"\w* \w brought|strong="H5148"\w* \w me|strong="H1288"\w* straight \w to|strong="H3068"\w* Abraham’s relatives, \w so|strong="H3808"\w* \w that|strong="H3068"\w* \w I|strong="H3808"\w* \w can|strong="H3808"\w* get \w a|strong="H3068"\w* wife \w for|strong="H3068"\w* Isaac.”   
\s1 Abraham’s worker talked to Rebekah’s family  
\p
\v 28 Rebekah \w ran|strong="H7323"\w* \w home|strong="H1004"\w* \w and|strong="H1004"\w* \w told|strong="H5046"\w* \w her|strong="H5046"\w* \w family|strong="H1004"\w* \w what|strong="H1697"\w* \w happened|strong="H1697"\w*.  
\v 29-30 She told them everything that Abraham’s worker said to her at the water-hole, and she showed them the gold nose ring and the gold bracelets that Abraham’s worker gave her. Rebekah’s brother Laban was there, and straight away he ran to the water-hole to find Abraham’s worker, and he found him standing there next to his camels.  
\v 31 \w Then|strong="H5975"\w* Laban said \w to|strong="H3068"\w* Abraham’s worker, “Sir, \w I|strong="H4100"\w* \w can|strong="H4100"\w* see \w that|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w good|strong="H4100"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w you|strong="H1288"\w*. Please, don’t keep \w on|strong="H3068"\w* \w standing|strong="H5975"\w* \w here|strong="H4725"\w* \w at|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* water-hole. Come \w home|strong="H1004"\w* \w with|strong="H1004"\w* \w me|strong="H1288"\w*. \w I|strong="H4100"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w room|strong="H1004"\w* ready \w for|strong="H3068"\w* \w you|strong="H1288"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w I|strong="H4100"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w place|strong="H4725"\w* \w for|strong="H3068"\w* \w your|strong="H3068"\w* \w camels|strong="H1581"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w stay|strong="H5975"\w* too.”   
\p
\v 32 \w So|strong="H5414"\w* Abraham’s worker, \w and|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* other men \w that|strong="H5414"\w* \w were|strong="H4325"\w* \w with|strong="H1004"\w* \w him|strong="H5414"\w*, \w they|strong="H7272"\w* \w went|strong="H1004"\w* \w to|strong="H5414"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* \w house|strong="H1004"\w* \w with|strong="H1004"\w* Laban. \w Then|strong="H5414"\w* \w they|strong="H7272"\w* \w took|strong="H5414"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* bags \w off|strong="H6605"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* \w camels|strong="H1581"\w*, \w and|strong="H1004"\w* Laban got \w food|strong="H4554"\w* \w for|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* \w camels|strong="H1581"\w* \w to|strong="H5414"\w* eat \w and|strong="H1004"\w* dry grass \w for|strong="H1004"\w* \w them|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H5414"\w* sleep \w on|strong="H1004"\w*. \w He|strong="H1004"\w* \w also|strong="H1581"\w* got \w water|strong="H4325"\w* \w so|strong="H5414"\w* \w that|strong="H5414"\w* Abraham’s worker \w and|strong="H1004"\w* \w his|strong="H5414"\w* men could \w wash|strong="H7364"\w* \w their|strong="H5414"\w* \w feet|strong="H7272"\w*.  
\v 33 \w After|strong="H5704"\w* \w that|strong="H1697"\w*, \w he|strong="H5704"\w* got Abraham’s worker \w and|strong="H6440"\w* \w his|strong="H6440"\w* men \w some|strong="H1697"\w* food. \w But|strong="H3808"\w* Abraham’s worker \w said|strong="H1696"\w*, “\w I|strong="H5704"\w* \w will|strong="H1697"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* eat \w yet|strong="H5704"\w*. \w First|strong="H6440"\w* \w I|strong="H5704"\w* \w have|strong="H1697"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w tell|strong="H1696"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w why|strong="H1697"\w* \w I|strong="H5704"\w* \w came|strong="H1697"\w* \w here|strong="H5704"\w*.”  
\p Laban \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w him|strong="H6440"\w*, “Yes, \w tell|strong="H1696"\w* \w us|strong="H6440"\w*.”   
\p
\v 34 \w So|strong="H5650"\w* Abraham’s worker talked \w to|strong="H5650"\w* Laban \w and|strong="H5650"\w* \w the|strong="H5650"\w* other people \w in|strong="H5650"\w* Rebekah’s family. He said, “\w I|strong="H5650"\w* work \w for|strong="H5650"\w* Abraham.  
\v 35 \w His|strong="H5414"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w really|strong="H3966"\w* \w good|strong="H3966"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w him|strong="H5414"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w now|strong="H5414"\w* Abraham \w is|strong="H3068"\w* \w very|strong="H3966"\w* \w rich|strong="H1431"\w*. Yes, \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w gave|strong="H5414"\w* \w him|strong="H5414"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* lot \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w sheep|strong="H6629"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w cows|strong="H1241"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w camels|strong="H1581"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w donkeys|strong="H2543"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* lot \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w silver|strong="H3701"\w* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w gold|strong="H2091"\w*. \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w also|strong="H3068"\w* \w gave|strong="H5414"\w* \w him|strong="H5414"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* lot \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w men|strong="H5650"\w* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w women|strong="H8198"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w work|strong="H5414"\w* \w for|strong="H3068"\w* \w him|strong="H5414"\w*.  
\v 36 \w And|strong="H1121"\w* Abraham \w has|strong="H3605"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w* too. Yes, Abraham’s wife \w Sarah|strong="H8283"\w* \w had|strong="H3205"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w baby|strong="H1121"\w* boy \w when|strong="H1121"\w* she \w was|strong="H1121"\w* very \w old|strong="H1121"\w*. \w That|strong="H3605"\w* boy \w is|strong="H3605"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w man|strong="H1121"\w* \w now|strong="H5414"\w*, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* later, \w when|strong="H1121"\w* Abraham dies, \w he|strong="H3605"\w* \w will|strong="H1121"\w* get \w everything|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* belonged \w to|strong="H5414"\w* Abraham.”   
\p
\v 37 \w Then|strong="H3947"\w* \w Abraham|strong="H3947"\w*’s worker said, “\w My|strong="H3947"\w* boss \w Abraham|strong="H3947"\w* \w got|strong="H3947"\w* \w me|strong="H3947"\w* \w to|strong="H1121"\w* \w make|strong="H3947"\w* \w him|strong="H3947"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* strong \w promise|strong="H7650"\w*. \w He|strong="H3808"\w* said, ‘\w Promise|strong="H7650"\w* \w me|strong="H3947"\w* \w that|strong="H1121"\w* \w you|strong="H3947"\w* \w will|strong="H1121"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w get|strong="H3947"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* wife \w for|strong="H3427"\w* \w my|strong="H3947"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w* \w from|strong="H1121"\w* \w this|strong="H3947"\w* country \w that|strong="H1121"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w are|strong="H1121"\w* \w living|strong="H3427"\w* \w in|strong="H3427"\w*. Don’t \w get|strong="H3947"\w* \w him|strong="H3947"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* wife \w from|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H3947"\w* \w Canaan|strong="H3669"\w* \w people|strong="H1121"\w* \w that|strong="H1121"\w* \w live|strong="H3427"\w* here.  
\v 38 \w No|strong="H3808"\w*, \w you|strong="H3947"\w* \w have|strong="H1121"\w* \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w go|strong="H3212"\w* \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w my|strong="H3947"\w* \w father|strong="H1121"\w*’s \w family|strong="H4940"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w my|strong="H3947"\w* other \w relatives|strong="H4940"\w*, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w get|strong="H3947"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* wife \w for|strong="H1004"\w* \w my|strong="H3947"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w*.’   
