\s1 Esau married 2 women  
\p
\v 34 Isaac \w and|strong="H1121"\w* Rebekah’s oldest \w son|strong="H1121"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* called \w Esau|strong="H6215"\w*. \w When|strong="H1961"\w* \w Esau|strong="H6215"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* 40 \w years|strong="H8141"\w* \w old|strong="H1121"\w*, \w he|strong="H8141"\w* \w married|strong="H3947"\w* 2 \w women|strong="H1323"\w*. \w One|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w those|strong="H1121"\w* \w women|strong="H1323"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* called \w Judith|strong="H3067"\w*. \w Her|strong="H3947"\w* \w father|strong="H1121"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* called Beeri, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w he|strong="H8141"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w from|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H3947"\w* Heth tribe. \w The|strong="H3947"\w* other \w woman|strong="H1323"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* called \w Basemath|strong="H1315"\w*. \w Her|strong="H3947"\w* \w father|strong="H1121"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* called Elon, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w he|strong="H8141"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w from|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H3947"\w* Heth tribe \w too|strong="H1961"\w*.  
\v 35 \w Those|strong="H1961"\w* 2 women \w gave|strong="H1961"\w* \w Isaac|strong="H3327"\w* \w and|strong="H3327"\w* \w Rebekah|strong="H7259"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* lot \w of|strong="H7307"\w* trouble, \w and|strong="H3327"\w* \w that|strong="H1961"\w* \w made|strong="H1961"\w* \w them|strong="H1961"\w* very sad.   
\c 27  
\s1 Rebekah and Jacob tricked Isaac  
\p
\v 1 \w A|strong="H3068"\w* \w long|strong="H1419"\w* \w time|strong="H1961"\w* \w later|strong="H1961"\w*, \w when|strong="H3588"\w* \w Isaac|strong="H3327"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w old|strong="H1121"\w*, \w his|strong="H7121"\w* \w eyes|strong="H5869"\w* got really weak \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w he|strong="H3588"\w* couldn’t \w see|strong="H7200"\w*. \w One|strong="H1121"\w* day, \w Isaac|strong="H3327"\w* \w sent|strong="H3327"\w* somebody \w to|strong="H1961"\w* get \w his|strong="H7121"\w* \w oldest|strong="H1419"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w* \w Esau|strong="H6215"\w*. \w Then|strong="H1961"\w* \w Esau|strong="H6215"\w* \w came|strong="H1961"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w him|strong="H7121"\w*, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w Isaac|strong="H3327"\w* \w said|strong="H7121"\w*, “\w My|strong="H7200"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w*.”  
\p \w And|strong="H1121"\w* \w Esau|strong="H6215"\w* \w said|strong="H7121"\w*, “\w Yes|strong="H3588"\w*, \w Father|strong="H1121"\w*?”   
\p
\v 2 \w And|strong="H3117"\w* Isaac said, “\w Listen|strong="H2009"\w*, \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w am|strong="H2204"\w* \w very|strong="H3045"\w* \w old|strong="H2204"\w*. Maybe \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w will|strong="H3808"\w* \w die|strong="H4194"\w* soon.  
\v 3-4 You are my oldest son, so you will be the next leader for our family. I have to do \w a|strong="H3068"\w* ceremony with you, to show that you will be the next leader. First, I want you to get your bow and arrows. Go out bush and kill \w a|strong="H3068"\w* wild animal, then cook it and make some good food for me, just the way I like it. Then bring me that food, and I will eat it. Then I will do that ceremony with you, to show that you are the next leader for our family. I will ask God to be good to you as the next leader for our family. I have to do that ceremony before I die.”   
\p
\v 5 \w Isaac|strong="H3327"\w*’s \w wife|strong="H1696"\w* \w Rebekah|strong="H7259"\w* \w was|strong="H3327"\w* nearby, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w she|strong="H3327"\w* \w heard|strong="H8085"\w* \w Isaac|strong="H3327"\w* \w say|strong="H1696"\w* \w those|strong="H8085"\w* things \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w Esau|strong="H6215"\w*. \w But|strong="H1696"\w* \w Isaac|strong="H3327"\w* didn’t know \w that|strong="H8085"\w* \w she|strong="H3327"\w* \w heard|strong="H8085"\w* \w him|strong="H8085"\w*.  
\p After \w that|strong="H8085"\w*, \w Esau|strong="H6215"\w* \w did|strong="H3327"\w* \w what|strong="H8085"\w* \w Isaac|strong="H3327"\w* \w told|strong="H1696"\w* \w him|strong="H8085"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w do|strong="H8085"\w*. \w He|strong="H1696"\w* got \w his|strong="H8085"\w* \w bow|strong="H1121"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w arrows|strong="H1121"\w*, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w he|strong="H1696"\w* \w went|strong="H3212"\w* \w out|strong="H3212"\w* bush \w to|strong="H1696"\w* look \w for|strong="H1121"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w wild|strong="H7704"\w* animal \w to|strong="H1696"\w* kill.   
\p
\v 6 Straight away, \w Rebekah|strong="H7259"\w* \w talked|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w her|strong="H3290"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w*. She \w said|strong="H1696"\w*, “\w I|strong="H2009"\w* \w heard|strong="H8085"\w* \w your|strong="H8085"\w* \w father|strong="H1121"\w* \w talk|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w your|strong="H8085"\w* brother \w Esau|strong="H6215"\w*.  
\v 7 \w Your|strong="H3068"\w* father said, ‘\w Go|strong="H3068"\w* \w and|strong="H3068"\w* kill \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w wild|strong="H6213"\w* animal \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w make|strong="H6213"\w* some \w good|strong="H6440"\w* \w food|strong="H4303"\w* \w for|strong="H6213"\w* \w me|strong="H6440"\w*. \w I|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* eat \w that|strong="H3068"\w* \w food|strong="H4303"\w*, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w then|strong="H6213"\w* \w I|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* ceremony \w with|strong="H3068"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w*. \w I|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* ask \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w be|strong="H3068"\w* \w good|strong="H6440"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w as|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* next leader \w for|strong="H6213"\w* \w our|strong="H3068"\w* family, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w I|strong="H3068"\w* know \w that|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* listen. \w I|strong="H3068"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w that|strong="H3068"\w* ceremony \w before|strong="H6440"\w* \w I|strong="H3068"\w* \w die|strong="H4194"\w*.’”   
\p
\v 8 \w Then|strong="H6258"\w* Rebekah \w said|strong="H8085"\w* \w to|strong="H8085"\w* Jacob, “\w My|strong="H8085"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w*, \w I|strong="H6258"\w* \w want|strong="H6963"\w* \w you|strong="H6680"\w* \w to|strong="H8085"\w* \w be|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* next leader \w for|strong="H1121"\w* \w our|strong="H8085"\w* family, \w not|strong="H8085"\w* \w your|strong="H8085"\w* brother Esau. \w So|strong="H6258"\w* \w listen|strong="H8085"\w* \w to|strong="H8085"\w* \w me|strong="H6963"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w do|strong="H6680"\w* \w what|strong="H6963"\w* \w I|strong="H6258"\w* \w say|strong="H6963"\w*.  
\v 9 \w Go|strong="H3212"\w* \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w the|strong="H3947"\w* \w place|strong="H8033"\w* \w where|strong="H8033"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w keep|strong="H6213"\w* \w our|strong="H3947"\w* \w goats|strong="H5795"\w*. \w Get|strong="H3947"\w* 2 really \w good|strong="H2896"\w* \w young|strong="H1423"\w* \w goats|strong="H5795"\w* \w and|strong="H3212"\w* \w bring|strong="H3947"\w* \w them|strong="H6213"\w* \w back|strong="H3947"\w* \w here|strong="H8033"\w*. \w I|strong="H6213"\w* \w will|strong="H6629"\w* cook \w those|strong="H6213"\w* \w goats|strong="H5795"\w* \w and|strong="H3212"\w* \w make|strong="H6213"\w* \w some|strong="H8033"\w* \w good|strong="H2896"\w* \w food|strong="H4303"\w* \w for|strong="H6213"\w* \w your|strong="H3947"\w* father, \w just|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H3947"\w* \w way|strong="H3212"\w* \w he|strong="H8033"\w* likes \w it|strong="H6213"\w*.  
\v 10 Then \w I|strong="H6440"\w* \w will|strong="H6440"\w* give \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w that|strong="H5668"\w* food \w to|strong="H6440"\w* take \w to|strong="H6440"\w* \w your|strong="H6440"\w* father. \w He|strong="H6440"\w* \w can|strong="H4194"\w*’t see, \w so|strong="H5668"\w* \w he|strong="H6440"\w* \w will|strong="H6440"\w* think \w that|strong="H5668"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w are|strong="H6440"\w* Esau, \w and|strong="H6440"\w* \w he|strong="H6440"\w* \w will|strong="H6440"\w* do \w that|strong="H5668"\w* ceremony \w with|strong="H6440"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w before|strong="H6440"\w* \w he|strong="H6440"\w* \w dies|strong="H4194"\w*. \w He|strong="H6440"\w* \w will|strong="H6440"\w* ask God \w to|strong="H6440"\w* \w be|strong="H1288"\w* \w good|strong="H6440"\w* \w to|strong="H6440"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w as|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* next leader \w for|strong="H6440"\w* \w our|strong="H1288"\w* family.”   
\p
\v 11 \w But|strong="H3290"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* said \w to|strong="H3290"\w* \w Rebekah|strong="H7259"\w*, “You know \w that|strong="H2005"\w* \w my|strong="H3290"\w* brother \w Esau|strong="H6215"\w* \w has|strong="H3290"\w* hair all over \w his|strong="H3290"\w* skin. \w But|strong="H3290"\w* \w I|strong="H2005"\w* have \w smooth|strong="H2509"\w* skin, \w I|strong="H2005"\w* don’t have any hair on \w my|strong="H3290"\w* skin.  
\v 12 Maybe \w my|strong="H5921"\w* father \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w touch|strong="H4959"\w* \w my|strong="H5921"\w* smooth skin, \w and|strong="H5869"\w* \w then|strong="H1961"\w* \w he|strong="H3808"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* know \w that|strong="H5869"\w* \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w am|strong="H1961"\w* Jacob, \w not|strong="H3808"\w* Esau. \w And|strong="H5869"\w* \w he|strong="H3808"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* know \w that|strong="H5869"\w* \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w am|strong="H1961"\w* tricking \w him|strong="H5921"\w*. \w Then|strong="H1961"\w* \w my|strong="H5921"\w* father \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* ask \w God|strong="H3808"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* \w good|strong="H5869"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w*. \w No|strong="H3808"\w*, \w he|strong="H3808"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* ask \w God|strong="H3808"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w curse|strong="H7045"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w*, \w and|strong="H5869"\w* \w God|strong="H3808"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* make trouble \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w*.”   
\p
\v 13 \w But|strong="H8085"\w* Rebekah \w said|strong="H8085"\w*, “Don’t worry. \w If|strong="H1121"\w* God wants \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w curse|strong="H7045"\w* \w you|strong="H5921"\w*, \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w will|strong="H1121"\w* ask \w him|strong="H5921"\w* \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w curse|strong="H7045"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w* \w instead|strong="H5921"\w*. Just \w do|strong="H8085"\w* \w what|strong="H6963"\w* \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w say|strong="H6963"\w*. \w Go|strong="H3212"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w get|strong="H3947"\w* \w those|strong="H5921"\w* 2 \w young|strong="H1121"\w* \w goats|strong="H1121"\w* \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w*.”   
\p
\v 14 \w So|strong="H6213"\w* Jacob \w went|strong="H3212"\w* \w and|strong="H3212"\w* \w got|strong="H3947"\w* 2 young goats, \w and|strong="H3212"\w* \w he|strong="H6213"\w* \w took|strong="H3947"\w* \w them|strong="H6213"\w* \w to|strong="H3212"\w* \w his|strong="H3947"\w* mother Rebekah. \w She|strong="H4303"\w* cooked \w those|strong="H6213"\w* goats, \w and|strong="H3212"\w* \w she|strong="H4303"\w* \w made|strong="H6213"\w* some good \w food|strong="H4303"\w*, \w just|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H3947"\w* \w way|strong="H3212"\w* Jacob’s father liked \w it|strong="H6213"\w*.  
