\v 18 Jacob took \w that|strong="H1121"\w* food, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w he|strong="H2009"\w* \w went|strong="H1121"\w* \w to|strong="H1121"\w* \w his|strong="H2009"\w* \w father|strong="H1121"\w* Isaac’s room. Jacob said, “\w Father|strong="H1121"\w*.” \w And|strong="H1121"\w* Isaac said, “\w Yes|strong="H2009"\w*, \w son|strong="H1121"\w*. \w Who|strong="H4310"\w* \w are|strong="H1121"\w* \w you|strong="H2009"\w*? \w Are|strong="H1121"\w* \w you|strong="H2009"\w* \w Esau|strong="H4310"\w*, \w or|strong="H1121"\w* \w are|strong="H1121"\w* \w you|strong="H2009"\w* Jacob?”   
\p
\v 19 \w Then|strong="H6965"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* lied \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w*, “\w I|strong="H5315"\w* am \w Esau|strong="H6215"\w*, \w your|strong="H6213"\w* older \w son|strong="H1060"\w*. \w I|strong="H5315"\w* killed \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w wild|strong="H6213"\w* animal \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w I|strong="H5315"\w* \w made|strong="H6213"\w* \w some|strong="H5315"\w* \w good|strong="H6965"\w* \w food|strong="H6718"\w* \w for|strong="H6213"\w* \w you|strong="H6213"\w*, \w just|strong="H6213"\w* \w like|strong="H6213"\w* \w you|strong="H6213"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w*. \w Sit|strong="H3427"\w* \w up|strong="H6965"\w* \w and|strong="H6965"\w* eat \w it|strong="H6213"\w*. \w Then|strong="H6965"\w* \w you|strong="H6213"\w* \w can|strong="H6213"\w* ask God \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w be|strong="H5315"\w* \w good|strong="H6965"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w me|strong="H4994"\w* \w as|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H6213"\w* next leader \w for|strong="H6213"\w* \w our|strong="H1288"\w* family.”   
\p
\v 20 \w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w Isaac|strong="H3327"\w* said, “\w My|strong="H3068"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w*, \w how|strong="H4100"\w* \w did|strong="H4100"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w get|strong="H4672"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* wild animal \w so|strong="H3588"\w* \w quickly|strong="H4116"\w*?”  
