\c 30  
\s1 Rachel’s working woman had 2 sons  
\p
\v 1 Leah already \w had|strong="H3205"\w* 4 \w kids|strong="H1121"\w* \w with|strong="H7065"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w*, \w but|strong="H3588"\w* \w her|strong="H7200"\w* sister \w Rachel|strong="H7354"\w* didn’t \w have|strong="H1121"\w* \w any|strong="H7200"\w* \w kids|strong="H1121"\w*. \w So|strong="H3808"\w* \w Rachel|strong="H7354"\w* got \w jealous|strong="H7065"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* Leah. \w Then|strong="H7200"\w* \w Rachel|strong="H7354"\w* said \w to|strong="H4191"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w*, “\w Give|strong="H3051"\w* \w me|strong="H7200"\w* \w kids|strong="H1121"\w*. \w If|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* don’t, \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H1121"\w* \w be|strong="H4191"\w* \w so|strong="H3808"\w* sad \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H1121"\w* \w die|strong="H4191"\w*.”   
