\v 12 \w And|strong="H5869"\w* \w he|strong="H3588"\w* said, ‘God says, “\w Look|strong="H7200"\w* \w at|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w male|strong="H6260"\w* \w goats|strong="H6260"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w are|strong="H5869"\w* joining \w together|strong="H5921"\w* \w with|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* female \w goats|strong="H6260"\w*. \w You|strong="H3588"\w* \w can|strong="H6213"\w* \w see|strong="H7200"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w those|strong="H3605"\w* \w male|strong="H6260"\w* \w goats|strong="H6260"\w* \w have|strong="H5869"\w* black \w and|strong="H5869"\w* white spots \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w their|strong="H3605"\w* wool. \w That|strong="H3588"\w* \w shows|strong="H6213"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* am helping \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w to|strong="H5927"\w* \w get|strong="H6213"\w* \w sheep|strong="H6629"\w* \w and|strong="H5869"\w* \w goats|strong="H6260"\w* \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w yourself|strong="H6213"\w*, \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* know \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w Laban|strong="H3837"\w* \w is|strong="H3605"\w* cheating \w you|strong="H3588"\w*.  
\v 13 \w I|strong="H6258"\w* am \w God|strong="H1008"\w*. \w A|strong="H3068"\w* long \w time|strong="H6258"\w* ago, \w I|strong="H6258"\w* \w came|strong="H3318"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w you|strong="H7725"\w* \w at|strong="H7725"\w* \w the|strong="H4480"\w* \w place|strong="H8033"\w* \w called|strong="H8033"\w* \w Bethel|strong="H1008"\w*. \w That|strong="H4480"\w*’s \w the|strong="H4480"\w* \w place|strong="H8033"\w* \w where|strong="H8033"\w* \w you|strong="H7725"\w* \w poured|strong="H4886"\w* olive \w oil|strong="H4886"\w* \w on|strong="H3318"\w* \w top|strong="H4480"\w* \w of|strong="H4480"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* stone \w to|strong="H7725"\w* show \w that|strong="H4480"\w* \w it|strong="H7725"\w* \w was|strong="H8033"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* special \w place|strong="H8033"\w*, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w you|strong="H7725"\w* \w made|strong="H5087"\w* promises \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w me|strong="H7725"\w*. \w Now|strong="H6258"\w* \w leave|strong="H3318"\w* \w this|strong="H2063"\w* country \w straight|strong="H3318"\w* \w away|strong="H7725"\w*, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w go|strong="H3318"\w* \w back|strong="H7725"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w your|strong="H7725"\w* \w home|strong="H7725"\w* country.” ’”\x * \xo 31:13 \xt Genesis 28:18-22\x*   
\p
\v 14 \w Then|strong="H6030"\w* \w Rachel|strong="H7354"\w* \w and|strong="H6030"\w* \w Leah|strong="H3812"\w* \w said|strong="H6030"\w* \w to|strong="H1004"\w* Jacob, “We \w will|strong="H1004"\w* \w go|strong="H6030"\w* \w with|strong="H1004"\w* \w you|strong="H6030"\w*. We don’t want \w to|strong="H1004"\w* live here \w with|strong="H1004"\w* \w our|strong="H5750"\w* father \w any|strong="H5750"\w* \w more|strong="H5750"\w*. \w He|strong="H1004"\w* \w will|strong="H1004"\w* never \w give|strong="H6030"\w* \w us|strong="H6030"\w* anything.  
\v 15 \w He|strong="H3588"\w* treats \w us|strong="H3588"\w* \w like|strong="H3808"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w are|strong="H1571"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w part|strong="H1571"\w* \w of|strong="H3701"\w* \w his|strong="H3588"\w* family. First, \w he|strong="H3588"\w* got \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w to|strong="H2803"\w* work \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w him|strong="H2803"\w* \w so|strong="H3808"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w could|strong="H1571"\w* marry \w us|strong="H3588"\w*. \w It|strong="H3588"\w*’s \w like|strong="H3808"\w* \w he|strong="H3588"\w* \w sold|strong="H4376"\w* \w us|strong="H3588"\w* \w to|strong="H2803"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w*. \w Then|strong="H1571"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* worked really hard \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w our|strong="H3588"\w* father, \w so|strong="H3808"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w he|strong="H3588"\w* got \w very|strong="H1571"\w* rich. \w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w our|strong="H3588"\w* father \w still|strong="H3588"\w* didn’t give \w us|strong="H3588"\w* \w anything|strong="H3808"\w*, \w even|strong="H1571"\w* \w though|strong="H3588"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w are|strong="H1571"\w* \w his|strong="H3588"\w* daughters. \w He|strong="H3588"\w* cheated \w us|strong="H3588"\w*, \w and|strong="H3701"\w* \w he|strong="H3588"\w* kept everything \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w himself|strong="H3808"\w*.  
\v 16 \w But|strong="H3588"\w* God \w took|strong="H5337"\w* \w away|strong="H5337"\w* \w some|strong="H3605"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w our|strong="H3605"\w* \w father|strong="H1121"\w*’s animals \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w gave|strong="H6213"\w* \w them|strong="H6213"\w* \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w*, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* got \w rich|strong="H6239"\w*. \w So|strong="H6213"\w* \w now|strong="H6258"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w those|strong="H3605"\w* animals \w and|strong="H1121"\w* good \w things|strong="H3605"\w*, \w they|strong="H3588"\w* belong \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w us|strong="H6213"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w our|strong="H3605"\w* \w kids|strong="H1121"\w*.”  
\p \w Then|strong="H6258"\w* Rachel \w and|strong="H1121"\w* Leah said \w to|strong="H6213"\w* Jacob, “\w Do|strong="H6213"\w* \w whatever|strong="H3605"\w* God \w told|strong="H6213"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w*.”   
\p
\v 17-19 So Jacob and his family got ready to leave. Laban wasn’t there at that time. He was cutting the wool off his sheep out in the grass lands, \w a|strong="H3068"\w* long way away. So Laban didn’t know that Jacob was getting ready to leave. And while Jacob was getting ready, Rachel went into Laban’s tent, and she stole some little statues that belonged to Laban. Sometimes, Laban and his family used to pray to those statues and ask them for help. They thought that those statues were gods that had power.  
\p Jacob went and got all his animals, and all the other things that he owned. You know, \w a|strong="H3068"\w* long time before this, when Jacob came to Laban’s home, he didn’t own anything. But now he owned lots and lots of things. So Jacob took all those things that he owned, and he put them on camels. Then he helped his kids and his wives to get on camels, and he got his other animals to walk in front of him, and they all left quickly to go to Canaan country. That’s the country where Jacob’s father Isaac lived.  
\v 20 \w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* tricked \w Laban|strong="H3837"\w*, \w he|strong="H1931"\w* didn’t \w tell|strong="H5046"\w* \w Laban|strong="H3837"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w he|strong="H1931"\w* \w left|strong="H1272"\w*.  
\p \w Laban|strong="H3837"\w* belonged \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* Aram tribe, \w and|strong="H3290"\w* \w his|strong="H5921"\w* country \w was|strong="H3820"\w* called Paddan Aram.  
\v 21 \w So|strong="H6965"\w* Jacob \w left|strong="H7760"\w* Paddan Aram \w country|strong="H2022"\w* \w with|strong="H6440"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* wives, \w his|strong="H3605"\w* kids, \w his|strong="H3605"\w* animals, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w everything|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w he|strong="H1931"\w* owned. \w They|strong="H1931"\w* \w crossed|strong="H5674"\w* \w over|strong="H5674"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w Euphrates|strong="H5104"\w* \w River|strong="H5104"\w*, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w then|strong="H6965"\w* \w they|strong="H1931"\w* \w started|strong="H6965"\w* \w to|strong="H6440"\w* \w go|strong="H5674"\w* south, towards \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w hill|strong="H2022"\w* \w country|strong="H2022"\w* \w called|strong="H7760"\w* \w Gilead|strong="H1568"\w*.   
\s1 Laban found Jacob  
\p
