\v 10 \w God|strong="H3068"\w*, \w you|strong="H7725"\w* \w are|strong="H3068"\w* \w my|strong="H3068"\w* boss. \w You|strong="H7725"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w been|strong="H3068"\w* \w very|strong="H3190"\w* \w good|strong="H3190"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w me|strong="H7725"\w*, just \w like|strong="H5973"\w* \w you|strong="H7725"\w* \w promised|strong="H3068"\w*. \w I|strong="H3068"\w* can always trust \w you|strong="H7725"\w*. \w You|strong="H7725"\w* \w did|strong="H3068"\w* lots \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w good|strong="H3190"\w* \w things|strong="H5973"\w* \w for|strong="H3068"\w* \w me|strong="H7725"\w*, \w even|strong="H3068"\w* though \w I|strong="H3068"\w*’m \w not|strong="H7725"\w* \w an|strong="H3068"\w* important person. \w When|strong="H7725"\w* \w I|strong="H3068"\w* \w left|strong="H7725"\w* \w my|strong="H3068"\w* \w home|strong="H7725"\w* country \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w I|strong="H3068"\w* crossed \w over|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* Jordan River, \w I|strong="H3068"\w* only \w had|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* walking stick \w with|strong="H5973"\w* \w me|strong="H7725"\w*. \w Now|strong="H3327"\w* \w I|strong="H3068"\w*’m \w going|strong="H7725"\w* \w back|strong="H7725"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w my|strong="H3068"\w* \w home|strong="H7725"\w* country, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w I|strong="H3068"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* lots \w and|strong="H3068"\w* lots \w of|strong="H3068"\w* people \w and|strong="H3068"\w* animals \w with|strong="H5973"\w* \w me|strong="H7725"\w*. Yes, \w I|strong="H3068"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* enough people \w and|strong="H3068"\w* animals \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w make|strong="H7725"\w* 2 camps.”   
\p
\v 11 \w Then|strong="H1961"\w* Jacob said \w to|strong="H1961"\w* God, “\w I|strong="H3588"\w*’m frightened \w of|strong="H5650"\w* \w my|strong="H3605"\w* brother Esau. Maybe \w he|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w come|strong="H1961"\w* \w and|strong="H5650"\w* attack \w me|strong="H6213"\w* \w and|strong="H5650"\w* kill \w me|strong="H6213"\w*, \w and|strong="H5650"\w* \w even|strong="H3588"\w* kill \w my|strong="H3605"\w* wives \w and|strong="H5650"\w* \w my|strong="H3605"\w* kids. God, please save \w us|strong="H6213"\w* \w from|strong="H1961"\w* \w my|strong="H3605"\w* brother.  
\v 12 Remember \w that|strong="H3588"\w* promise \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w made|strong="H5221"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w me|strong="H4994"\w*. \w You|strong="H3588"\w* said, ‘\w I|strong="H3588"\w* promise \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H1121"\w* \w be|strong="H3027"\w* good \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w*, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H1121"\w* \w give|strong="H4994"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* really big family. Lots \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w kids|strong="H1121"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* grand-kids \w will|strong="H1121"\w* \w be|strong="H3027"\w* \w born|strong="H1121"\w* \w into|strong="H5921"\w* \w your|strong="H5921"\w* family later \w on|strong="H5921"\w*, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w they|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H1121"\w* \w become|strong="H3027"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* really big mob \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w people|strong="H1121"\w*. Nobody \w will|strong="H1121"\w* \w be|strong="H3027"\w* \w able|strong="H3027"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* count \w them|strong="H5921"\w*, just \w like|strong="H1121"\w* nobody \w can|strong="H1121"\w* count \w all|strong="H5337"\w* \w those|strong="H1121"\w* little bits \w of|strong="H1121"\w* sand \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w are|strong="H1121"\w* \w at|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* beaches \w by|strong="H3027"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* sea.’ \w Please|strong="H4994"\w* \w be|strong="H3027"\w* good \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w me|strong="H4994"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w my|strong="H5921"\w* family, \w God|strong="H3027"\w*, just \w like|strong="H1121"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* promised. \w Please|strong="H4994"\w* don’t \w let|strong="H4994"\w* \w my|strong="H5921"\w* brother \w kill|strong="H5221"\w* \w us|strong="H4994"\w*.”\x * \xo 32:12 \xt Genesis 22:17\x*   
\p
\v 13 \w Jacob|strong="H5608"\w* stayed \w in|strong="H3220"\w* \w that|strong="H3808"\w* \w place|strong="H7760"\w* \w that|strong="H3808"\w* night. \w He|strong="H3808"\w* wanted \w to|strong="H3220"\w* \w give|strong="H7760"\w* \w his|strong="H7760"\w* brother Esau \w a|strong="H3068"\w* present, \w so|strong="H3808"\w* \w he|strong="H3808"\w* picked some \w of|strong="H2233"\w* \w his|strong="H7760"\w* animals \w to|strong="H3220"\w* \w give|strong="H7760"\w* \w to|strong="H3220"\w* Esau.  
