\v 17 \w Then|strong="H5414"\w* Jacob talked \w to|strong="H5414"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* work-man \w that|strong="H5414"\w* \w was|strong="H3027"\w* \w in|strong="H6440"\w* \w charge|strong="H3027"\w* \w of|strong="H3027"\w* \w that|strong="H5414"\w* 1st group \w of|strong="H3027"\w* animals. \w He|strong="H5414"\w* said, “\w You|strong="H5414"\w* \w are|strong="H3027"\w* \w going|strong="H5674"\w* \w to|strong="H5414"\w* \w meet|strong="H6440"\w* \w my|strong="H5414"\w* brother Esau \w first|strong="H6440"\w*. \w I|strong="H5414"\w* reckon \w he|strong="H5414"\w* \w will|strong="H5650"\w* say \w to|strong="H5414"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w*, ‘\w Who|strong="H5650"\w* \w is|strong="H3027"\w* \w your|strong="H5414"\w* boss? \w Where|strong="H3027"\w* \w are|strong="H3027"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* \w going|strong="H5674"\w*? \w And|strong="H3027"\w* \w who|strong="H5650"\w* \w do|strong="H3027"\w* \w these|strong="H7760"\w* animals belong \w to|strong="H5414"\w*?’  
