\p Jacob \w thought|strong="H1697"\w*, “Maybe \w my|strong="H3605"\w* brother \w will|strong="H1571"\w* stop being angry \w with|strong="H1980"\w* \w me|strong="H1696"\w*, \w because|strong="H1697"\w* \w I|strong="H1697"\w*’m sending \w my|strong="H3605"\w* work-men \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w give|strong="H6680"\w* \w him|strong="H4672"\w* presents. \w They|strong="H1697"\w* \w will|strong="H1571"\w* \w give|strong="H6680"\w* \w him|strong="H4672"\w* \w those|strong="H3605"\w* presents, \w and|strong="H1980"\w* \w then|strong="H1980"\w* \w I|strong="H1697"\w* \w will|strong="H1571"\w* \w go|strong="H1980"\w* \w and|strong="H1980"\w* \w meet|strong="H4672"\w* \w him|strong="H4672"\w*. Maybe \w he|strong="H3605"\w* \w will|strong="H1571"\w* \w be|strong="H1697"\w* friendly \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w me|strong="H1696"\w*.”   
\p
\v 21 \w So|strong="H3651"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* \w sent|strong="H1980"\w* \w his|strong="H5375"\w* work-men \w to|strong="H1980"\w* \w give|strong="H7200"\w* \w those|strong="H3588"\w* animals \w to|strong="H1980"\w* \w his|strong="H5375"\w* brother Esau. \w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* stayed \w in|strong="H1980"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* camp.   
\s1 A man wrestled with Jacob  
\p
\v 22-23 That same night, Jacob got his 2 wives, and his 2 working women, and his 11 sons, and all the other men and women in his camp, and all the animals, and everything that he owned, and they left the camp, and they crossed over the Jabbok River. They all crossed over at \w a|strong="H3068"\w* place where the river wasn’t deep.  
\v 24 \w But|strong="H3947"\w* Jacob didn’t \w go|strong="H5674"\w* \w with|strong="H3947"\w* \w them|strong="H3947"\w*. \w He|strong="H3947"\w* stayed next \w to|strong="H5674"\w* \w the|strong="H3947"\w* \w river|strong="H5158"\w*, \w and|strong="H3947"\w* \w he|strong="H3947"\w* was \w all|strong="H3947"\w* alone.  
\p \w Then|strong="H3947"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w man|strong="H5674"\w* \w came|strong="H5674"\w* \w and|strong="H3947"\w* grabbed Jacob, \w and|strong="H3947"\w* \w that|strong="H5158"\w* \w man|strong="H5674"\w* wrestled \w with|strong="H3947"\w* Jacob. \w They|strong="H3947"\w* kept \w on|strong="H5674"\w* wrestling \w all|strong="H3947"\w* night, until \w it|strong="H3947"\w* was nearly time \w for|strong="H3947"\w* \w the|strong="H3947"\w* sun \w to|strong="H5674"\w* \w come|strong="H5674"\w* \w up|strong="H3947"\w*.\x * \xo 32:24 \xt Hosea 12:3-4\x*\fig A man wrestled with Jacob|src="CO00686B.TIF" size="col" copy="David C Cook" ref="32:24" \fig*  
\v 25 \w That|strong="H5704"\w* other man \w saw|strong="H3290"\w* \w that|strong="H5704"\w* \w he|strong="H5704"\w* couldn’t win, \w so|strong="H5927"\w* \w he|strong="H5704"\w* touched \w the|strong="H5704"\w* joint \w at|strong="H5927"\w* \w the|strong="H5704"\w* top \w of|strong="H3498"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w*’s leg, \w and|strong="H5927"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w*’s leg bone \w came|strong="H5927"\w* \w out|strong="H5704"\w* \w of|strong="H3498"\w* \w the|strong="H5704"\w* joint \w while|strong="H5704"\w* \w they|strong="H5704"\w* \w were|strong="H3290"\w* wrestling.  
\v 26 \w Then|strong="H7200"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w man|strong="H7200"\w* said \w to|strong="H3201"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w*, “\w Let|strong="H3808"\w* \w me|strong="H7200"\w* \w go|strong="H3201"\w*. \w It|strong="H3588"\w*’s nearly time \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* sun \w to|strong="H3201"\w* \w come|strong="H5060"\w* \w up|strong="H7200"\w*.”  
\p \w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* said, “\w No|strong="H3808"\w*. First, \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w want|strong="H3808"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w to|strong="H3201"\w* promise \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3808"\w* \w make|strong="H7200"\w* \w things|strong="H5973"\w* \w go|strong="H3201"\w* \w well|strong="H5973"\w* \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w me|strong="H7200"\w*. \w Then|strong="H7200"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3808"\w* \w let|strong="H3808"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w go|strong="H3201"\w*.”   
\p
\v 27 \w The|strong="H3588"\w* man said, “\w What|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H1288"\w* \w your|strong="H3588"\w* name?”  
\p \w And|strong="H7971"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H7971"\w* said, “\w My|strong="H7971"\w* name \w is|strong="H1288"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H7971"\w*.”   
\p
