\c 33  
\s1 Jacob met Esau again  
\p
\v 1 \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* \w and|strong="H3967"\w* \w his|strong="H5375"\w* family kept \w on|strong="H5921"\w* walking towards \w the|strong="H5921"\w* place \w where|strong="H5921"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w*’s brother \w Esau|strong="H6215"\w* \w was|strong="H3206"\w*. \w Then|strong="H2009"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* \w looked|strong="H7200"\w* \w up|strong="H5375"\w* \w and|strong="H3967"\w* \w saw|strong="H7200"\w* \w Esau|strong="H6215"\w* \w coming|strong="H2009"\w* towards \w him|strong="H5921"\w* \w with|strong="H5973"\w* 400 \w men|strong="H3206"\w*. \w So|strong="H5375"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* stopped walking, \w and|strong="H3967"\w* \w he|strong="H8147"\w* split \w up|strong="H5375"\w* \w his|strong="H5375"\w* family \w into|strong="H5921"\w* groups. \w He|strong="H8147"\w* \w put|strong="H5375"\w* \w his|strong="H5375"\w* wife \w Leah|strong="H3812"\w* \w with|strong="H5973"\w* \w her|strong="H5375"\w* kids, \w and|strong="H3967"\w* \w he|strong="H8147"\w* \w put|strong="H5375"\w* \w his|strong="H5375"\w* wife \w Rachel|strong="H7354"\w* \w with|strong="H5973"\w* \w her|strong="H5375"\w* son Joseph, \w and|strong="H3967"\w* \w he|strong="H8147"\w* \w put|strong="H5375"\w* \w his|strong="H5375"\w* 2 working \w women|strong="H8198"\w* \w with|strong="H5973"\w* \w their|strong="H5375"\w* kids.  
