\s1 Jacob went back to Canaan country  
\p
\v 18 \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* \w was|strong="H5892"\w* born \w in|strong="H2583"\w* \w Canaan|strong="H3667"\w* country, \w and|strong="H5892"\w* \w he|strong="H6440"\w* grew up \w there|strong="H6440"\w*. \w But|strong="H3290"\w* then \w he|strong="H6440"\w* \w went|strong="H3290"\w* \w to|strong="H6440"\w* \w Paddan|strong="H6307"\w* \w Aram|strong="H6307"\w* country \w for|strong="H6440"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w long|strong="H6440"\w* \w time|strong="H6440"\w*. Now \w he|strong="H6440"\w* finally got back \w to|strong="H6440"\w* \w his|strong="H6440"\w* home country \w again|strong="H6440"\w*. \w When|strong="H3290"\w* \w he|strong="H6440"\w* got \w there|strong="H6440"\w*, \w he|strong="H6440"\w* \w set|strong="H3290"\w* up \w his|strong="H6440"\w* \w camp|strong="H2583"\w* \w on|strong="H5892"\w* some \w land|strong="H6440"\w* outside \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w town|strong="H5892"\w* called Shekem.  
\v 19 \w That|strong="H1121"\w* \w land|strong="H7704"\w* \w where|strong="H8033"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H8033"\w* \w put|strong="H5186"\w* \w his|strong="H5186"\w* tent, \w it|strong="H5186"\w* belonged \w to|strong="H3027"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w man|strong="H1121"\w* \w called|strong="H8033"\w* Shekem \w and|strong="H3967"\w* \w his|strong="H5186"\w* \w brothers|strong="H1121"\w*. \w Their|strong="H5186"\w* \w father|strong="H1121"\w* \w was|strong="H1121"\w* \w called|strong="H8033"\w* \w Hamor|strong="H2544"\w*. \w And|strong="H3967"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H8033"\w* \w bought|strong="H7069"\w* \w that|strong="H1121"\w* \w land|strong="H7704"\w* \w from|strong="H3027"\w* Shekem \w and|strong="H3967"\w* \w his|strong="H5186"\w* \w brothers|strong="H1121"\w*. \w He|strong="H8033"\w* \w paid|strong="H3027"\w* \w them|strong="H3027"\w* 100 \w pieces|strong="H7192"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w silver|strong="H7192"\w* \w money|strong="H7192"\w* \w for|strong="H3027"\w* \w that|strong="H1121"\w* \w land|strong="H7704"\w*.\x * \xo 33:19 \xt Joshua 24:32; John 4:5\x*  
\v 20 \w Then|strong="H7121"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H8033"\w* piled \w up|strong="H5324"\w* stones \w there|strong="H8033"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w make|strong="H7121"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* special table \w with|strong="H3478"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* flat top, \w so|strong="H7121"\w* \w that|strong="H3478"\w* \w he|strong="H8033"\w* could burn animals \w to|strong="H3478"\w* show respect \w to|strong="H3478"\w* God. \w And|strong="H3478"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H8033"\w* \w called|strong="H7121"\w* \w it|strong="H7121"\w* \em The God of Israel is God\em*.   
\c 34  
\s1 Shekem’s mob tried to make an agreement with Jacob’s mob  
\p
\v 1-2 This story is about what happened to Jacob’s family in the town called Shekem, in Canaan country. The big boss of that town was called Hamor, and he was from the Hiv tribe. And Hamor had \w a|strong="H3068"\w* son called Shekem.  
\p Jacob and Leah’s daughter was called Dinah, and she was \w a|strong="H3068"\w* young woman. One day, she went out to visit some other women that lived in that place. But that man Shekem, he saw Dinah, and he wanted to have her for himself. So he grabbed Dinah and he made her sleep with him, like \w a|strong="H3068"\w* woman sleeps with her husband. Shekem really shamed Dinah.   
\p
\v 3 Shekem \w fell|strong="H5921"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* love \w with|strong="H1696"\w* \w Dinah|strong="H1783"\w*, \w and|strong="H3290"\w* \w he|strong="H5921"\w* \w thought|strong="H3820"\w* \w that|strong="H5315"\w* \w she|strong="H5921"\w* \w was|strong="H3820"\w* wonderful. \w So|strong="H1696"\w* \w he|strong="H5921"\w* \w talked|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w her|strong="H5921"\w* \w and|strong="H3290"\w* tried \w to|strong="H1696"\w* get \w her|strong="H5921"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* love \w him|strong="H5921"\w* \w too|strong="H5921"\w*.  
\v 4 \w Then|strong="H3947"\w* Shekem talked \w to|strong="H3947"\w* \w his|strong="H3947"\w* father \w Hamor|strong="H2544"\w* \w and|strong="H3947"\w* said, “I want \w to|strong="H3947"\w* \w marry|strong="H3947"\w* \w that|strong="H2063"\w* woman. Ask \w her|strong="H3947"\w* father \w to|strong="H3947"\w* \w give|strong="H3947"\w* \w her|strong="H3947"\w* \w to|strong="H3947"\w* \w me|strong="H3947"\w*, \w so|strong="H3947"\w* \w that|strong="H2063"\w* \w she|strong="H2063"\w* \w can|strong="H3947"\w* be \w my|strong="H3947"\w* wife.”   
\p
\v 5 \w At|strong="H1961"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w time|strong="H1961"\w*, \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w in|strong="H8085"\w* \w his|strong="H8085"\w* camp, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w*’s \w sons|strong="H1121"\w* \w were|strong="H1961"\w* \w out|strong="H5704"\w* \w in|strong="H8085"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* grass \w lands|strong="H7704"\w* \w looking|strong="H1961"\w* \w after|strong="H1961"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w*’s \w animals|strong="H1961"\w*. \w Then|strong="H1961"\w* somebody \w went|strong="H3290"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w told|strong="H8085"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* Shekem \w did|strong="H3290"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* bad \w thing|strong="H3588"\w* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w his|strong="H8085"\w* \w daughter|strong="H1323"\w* \w Dinah|strong="H1783"\w*. \w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* didn’t say anything, \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \w he|strong="H3588"\w* wanted \w to|strong="H5704"\w* wait \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w his|strong="H8085"\w* \w sons|strong="H1121"\w* \w to|strong="H5704"\w* \w come|strong="H1961"\w* home.   
\p
\v 6-7 Then somebody went and told Jacob’s sons that Shekem did that bad thing to Dinah. So Jacob’s sons got really upset and angry. They said, “Shekem slept with our sister. That was \w a|strong="H3068"\w* properly wrong thing that he did. He made our family shamed.” And Jacob’s sons left the grass lands, and they quickly went back to Jacob’s camp.  
\p Hamor, Shekem’s father, he went to Jacob’s camp to talk to Jacob, and Shekem went with him.  
\v 8 \w And|strong="H1121"\w* \w Hamor|strong="H2544"\w* \w talked|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* Jacob \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w his|strong="H5414"\w* \w sons|strong="H1121"\w*. \w Hamor|strong="H2544"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w*, “\w My|strong="H5414"\w* \w son|strong="H1121"\w* Shekem, \w he|strong="H5414"\w* loves \w your|strong="H5414"\w* \w daughter|strong="H1323"\w* Dinah, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w he|strong="H5414"\w* really wants \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w marry|strong="H5414"\w* \w her|strong="H5414"\w*. \w Please|strong="H4994"\w* \w give|strong="H5414"\w* \w her|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w him|strong="H5414"\w*, \w so|strong="H5414"\w* \w that|strong="H5315"\w* she \w can|strong="H1121"\w* \w be|strong="H1121"\w* \w his|strong="H5414"\w* \w wife|strong="H1696"\w*.  
\v 9 \w And|strong="H1323"\w* \w let|strong="H5414"\w*’s \w make|strong="H5414"\w* \w an|strong="H5414"\w* agreement between \w our|strong="H5414"\w* families. \w Let|strong="H5414"\w*’s agree \w that|strong="H5414"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* \w men|strong="H3947"\w* \w in|strong="H5414"\w* \w my|strong="H5414"\w* family \w can|strong="H3947"\w* \w marry|strong="H3947"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* \w women|strong="H1323"\w* \w in|strong="H5414"\w* \w your|strong="H5414"\w* family, \w and|strong="H1323"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* \w men|strong="H3947"\w* \w in|strong="H5414"\w* \w your|strong="H5414"\w* family \w can|strong="H3947"\w* \w marry|strong="H3947"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* \w women|strong="H1323"\w* \w in|strong="H5414"\w* \w my|strong="H5414"\w* family.  
\v 10 \w You|strong="H6440"\w* mob can \w live|strong="H3427"\w* \w in|strong="H3427"\w* \w our|strong="H1961"\w* \w land|strong="H6440"\w*, \w and|strong="H6440"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* can do whatever \w you|strong="H6440"\w* want here. \w You|strong="H6440"\w* can buy \w things|strong="H1961"\w* \w and|strong="H6440"\w* sell \w things|strong="H1961"\w* here, \w and|strong="H6440"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* can even buy some \w of|strong="H3427"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w land|strong="H6440"\w* \w for|strong="H6440"\w* yourself.”   
\p
\v 11 \w Then|strong="H5414"\w* Shekem talked \w to|strong="H5414"\w* Dinah’s father Jacob \w and|strong="H5869"\w* \w her|strong="H5414"\w* brothers. \w He|strong="H5414"\w* said, “Please \w be|strong="H5869"\w* \w good|strong="H5869"\w* \w to|strong="H5414"\w* \w me|strong="H5414"\w* \w and|strong="H5869"\w* \w do|strong="H5869"\w* what \w I|strong="H5414"\w* ask, \w and|strong="H5869"\w* \w I|strong="H5414"\w* \w will|strong="H5869"\w* \w give|strong="H5414"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* whatever \w you|strong="H5414"\w* want.”   
\p
\v 12 \w In|strong="H5921"\w* \w that|strong="H5414"\w* culture, \w when|strong="H7235"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* man married \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w woman|strong="H5291"\w*, \w he|strong="H5414"\w* \w used|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w pay|strong="H5414"\w* money \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w that|strong="H5414"\w* \w woman|strong="H5291"\w*’s family \w and|strong="H3966"\w* \w give|strong="H5414"\w* \w them|strong="H5414"\w* presents. \w So|strong="H5414"\w* Shekem talked \w to|strong="H5921"\w* Dinah’s father \w and|strong="H3966"\w* brothers \w about|strong="H5921"\w* \w that|strong="H5414"\w*. \w He|strong="H5414"\w* said, “Tell \w me|strong="H5414"\w* how \w much|strong="H7235"\w* money \w you|strong="H5414"\w* want, \w and|strong="H3966"\w* \w I|strong="H5414"\w* \w will|strong="H5414"\w* \w give|strong="H5414"\w* \w it|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w*. \w Even|strong="H5921"\w* if \w you|strong="H5414"\w* want lots \w and|strong="H3966"\w* lots \w of|strong="H5921"\w* money \w and|strong="H3966"\w* presents, \w I|strong="H5414"\w* \w will|strong="H5414"\w* \w give|strong="H5414"\w* \w them|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w*. Please just \w let|strong="H5414"\w* \w me|strong="H5414"\w* \w marry|strong="H5921"\w* \w that|strong="H5414"\w* \w young|strong="H5291"\w* \w woman|strong="H5291"\w* Dinah.”   
\p
\v 13 \w But|strong="H6030"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w*’s \w sons|strong="H1121"\w* \w were|strong="H1121"\w* still thinking \w about|strong="H1696"\w* \w that|strong="H1121"\w* bad thing \w that|strong="H1121"\w* Shekem \w did|strong="H3290"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w their|strong="H3290"\w* sister \w Dinah|strong="H1783"\w*. \w So|strong="H1696"\w* \w they|strong="H4820"\w* pretended \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w make|strong="H2930"\w* \w an|strong="H6030"\w* agreement \w with|strong="H1696"\w* Shekem \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w Hamor|strong="H2544"\w*, \w but|strong="H6030"\w* really, \w they|strong="H4820"\w* \w were|strong="H1121"\w* tricking \w them|strong="H1121"\w*.  
\v 14 Jacob’s sons \w said|strong="H1697"\w*, “\w You|strong="H3588"\w* know, \w all|strong="H6213"\w* \w of|strong="H1697"\w* \w us|strong="H5414"\w* \w men|strong="H6213"\w* \w and|strong="H6213"\w* boys \w in|strong="H6213"\w* \w our|strong="H5414"\w* mob, \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w had|strong="H3588"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* young \w man|strong="H2088"\w* operation. \w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* mob don’t \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* operation \w on|strong="H6213"\w* \w your|strong="H5414"\w* boys. \w We|strong="H3588"\w* \w can|strong="H3201"\w*’t \w let|strong="H5414"\w* \w our|strong="H5414"\w* sister \w marry|strong="H5414"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w man|strong="H2088"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* didn’t \w have|strong="H1697"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* operation. \w That|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H1697"\w* \w make|strong="H6213"\w* \w our|strong="H5414"\w* family shamed.  
\v 15 \w So|strong="H1961"\w* \w listen|strong="H3605"\w*, \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* make \w an|strong="H1961"\w* agreement \w with|strong="H3605"\w* \w you|strong="H3605"\w* mob. \w You|strong="H3605"\w* \w and|strong="H2145"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w men|strong="H2145"\w* \w and|strong="H2145"\w* boys \w in|strong="H2145"\w* \w your|strong="H3605"\w* mob, \w you|strong="H3605"\w* \w have|strong="H1961"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w have|strong="H1961"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* young \w man|strong="H2145"\w* operation. \w Then|strong="H1961"\w* \w you|strong="H3605"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* \w like|strong="H3644"\w* \w us|strong="H1961"\w*.  
\v 16 \w If|strong="H1961"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w* agree \w to|strong="H1961"\w* do \w that|strong="H5971"\w*, \w then|strong="H1961"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w let|strong="H5414"\w* \w our|strong="H5414"\w* sister \w marry|strong="H3947"\w* Shekem. We \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w let|strong="H5414"\w* \w our|strong="H5414"\w* \w women|strong="H1323"\w* \w marry|strong="H3947"\w* \w your|strong="H5414"\w* \w men|strong="H5971"\w*, \w and|strong="H5971"\w* \w our|strong="H5414"\w* \w men|strong="H5971"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w marry|strong="H3947"\w* \w your|strong="H5414"\w* \w women|strong="H1323"\w*. We \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w live|strong="H3427"\w* \w with|strong="H3427"\w* \w you|strong="H5414"\w*, \w and|strong="H5971"\w* \w our|strong="H5414"\w* mob \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w join|strong="H3427"\w* \w together|strong="H5971"\w* \w with|strong="H3427"\w* \w your|strong="H5414"\w* mob, \w and|strong="H5971"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w become|strong="H1961"\w* \w one|strong="H1961"\w* tribe.  
