\v 29 \w They|strong="H3605"\w* \w took|strong="H7617"\w* \w everything|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w was|strong="H1004"\w* \w in|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w houses|strong="H1004"\w*. \w And|strong="H1004"\w* \w they|strong="H3605"\w* got \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* women \w and|strong="H1004"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* young kids, \w and|strong="H1004"\w* \w they|strong="H3605"\w* \w took|strong="H7617"\w* \w them|strong="H7617"\w* \w away|strong="H7617"\w*, \w like|strong="H1004"\w* \w they|strong="H3605"\w* \w were|strong="H2428"\w* prisoners.   
\p
\v 30 \w Then|strong="H5221"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* talked strongly \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w his|strong="H5921"\w* sons \w Simeon|strong="H8095"\w* \w and|strong="H1004"\w* \w Levi|strong="H3878"\w*. \w He|strong="H1004"\w* said, “\w You|strong="H5921"\w* \w made|strong="H5221"\w* big \w trouble|strong="H5916"\w* \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w me|strong="H5921"\w*. \w You|strong="H5921"\w* know \w about|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* other tribes \w that|strong="H3669"\w* \w live|strong="H3427"\w* \w in|strong="H3427"\w* \w this|strong="H1004"\w* land, \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w Canaan|strong="H3669"\w* tribe \w and|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* Periz tribe. Well, \w now|strong="H5921"\w* \w those|strong="H5921"\w* tribes \w will|strong="H1004"\w* hate \w us|strong="H5921"\w*, \w because|strong="H5921"\w* \w you|strong="H5921"\w* finished \w up|strong="H5921"\w* Shekem’s mob. \w And|strong="H1004"\w* maybe \w those|strong="H5921"\w* tribes \w will|strong="H1004"\w* \w join|strong="H3427"\w* \w together|strong="H5921"\w* \w and|strong="H1004"\w* \w attack|strong="H5221"\w* \w us|strong="H5921"\w*. \w My|strong="H5921"\w* mob \w is|strong="H1004"\w* \w small|strong="H4962"\w*, \w so|strong="H3427"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H1004"\w* not \w be|strong="H1004"\w* able \w to|strong="H5921"\w* fight \w those|strong="H5921"\w* big tribes, \w and|strong="H1004"\w* \w then|strong="H5221"\w* \w they|strong="H5921"\w* \w will|strong="H1004"\w* finish \w us|strong="H5921"\w* \w up|strong="H5921"\w*, \w me|strong="H5921"\w* \w and|strong="H1004"\w* \w my|strong="H5921"\w* \w family|strong="H1004"\w*.”   
\p
\v 31 But Simeon \w and|strong="H6213"\w* Levi said, “\w That|strong="H6213"\w* man \w did|strong="H6213"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* bad thing \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w our|strong="H6213"\w* sister. \w He|strong="H6213"\w* \w made|strong="H6213"\w* \w her|strong="H6213"\w* sleep \w with|strong="H6213"\w* \w him|strong="H6213"\w*, \w like|strong="H6213"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* woman sleeps \w with|strong="H6213"\w* \w her|strong="H6213"\w* husband, \w and|strong="H6213"\w* \w then|strong="H6213"\w* \w he|strong="H6213"\w* \w tried|strong="H6213"\w* \w to|strong="H6213"\w* pay \w us|strong="H6213"\w* money \w for|strong="H6213"\w* \w her|strong="H6213"\w*. Somebody \w had|strong="H6213"\w* \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* payback \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w his|strong="H6213"\w* mob.”   
\c 35  
\s1 Jacob went back to Bethel  
\p
\v 1 \w Then|strong="H6965"\w* \w God|strong="H1008"\w* said \w to|strong="H5927"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w*, “\w Leave|strong="H5927"\w* \w this|strong="H6213"\w* \w place|strong="H3427"\w*, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w go|strong="H5927"\w* \w to|strong="H5927"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* special \w place|strong="H3427"\w* \w called|strong="H8033"\w* \w Bethel|strong="H1008"\w*. Remember, \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w long|strong="H6440"\w* \w time|strong="H6440"\w* ago, \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w ran|strong="H1272"\w* \w away|strong="H1272"\w* \w from|strong="H6440"\w* \w your|strong="H6440"\w* brother \w Esau|strong="H6215"\w*, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w went|strong="H5927"\w* \w to|strong="H5927"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w place|strong="H3427"\w*, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w I|strong="H7200"\w* \w came|strong="H5927"\w* \w to|strong="H5927"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w there|strong="H8033"\w*. Now \w I|strong="H7200"\w* want \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w to|strong="H5927"\w* \w go|strong="H5927"\w* \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w live|strong="H3427"\w* \w in|strong="H3427"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w place|strong="H3427"\w*, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w I|strong="H7200"\w* want \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w to|strong="H5927"\w* pile \w up|strong="H5927"\w* stones \w there|strong="H8033"\w*, \w to|strong="H5927"\w* \w make|strong="H6213"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* special \w table|strong="H6440"\w*. \w Then|strong="H6965"\w* \w I|strong="H7200"\w* want \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w to|strong="H5927"\w* \w burn|strong="H5927"\w* animals \w on|strong="H7200"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* special \w table|strong="H6440"\w*, \w to|strong="H5927"\w* \w show|strong="H7200"\w* \w respect|strong="H7200"\w* \w to|strong="H5927"\w* \w me|strong="H6440"\w*, \w because|strong="H6440"\w* \w I|strong="H7200"\w* am \w God|strong="H1008"\w*.”   
\p
\v 2-3 So Jacob talked to his family, and to all the other people that were in his camp. He said, “We are going to leave this place and go to the place called Bethel. I’m going to make \w a|strong="H3068"\w* special table there, so that I can burn animals to show respect to God. You know, God is the one that helped me every time I got trouble, and he stayed with me wherever I went.”  
\p Jacob kept on talking to his mob. He said, “Some of you mob have little statues with you, that came from other countries. Some people think that those statues are gods that have power. You mob have to get rid of those statues. Then you all have to wash your bodies and put on clean clothes, because \w we|strong="H3068"\w* are going to \w a|strong="H3068"\w* special place to show respect to God.”   
\p
\v 4 \w So|strong="H5414"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w*’s family, \w and|strong="H3027"\w* everybody \w else|strong="H3027"\w* \w in|strong="H3027"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w*’s camp, \w they|strong="H3027"\w* \w went|strong="H3290"\w* \w and|strong="H3027"\w* got \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w their|strong="H3605"\w* little statues, \w and|strong="H3027"\w* \w they|strong="H3027"\w* \w gave|strong="H5414"\w* \w them|strong="H5414"\w* \w to|strong="H5414"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w*. \w They|strong="H3027"\w* \w also|strong="H3027"\w* \w took|strong="H5414"\w* \w out|strong="H5414"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w rings|strong="H5141"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w were|strong="H3027"\w* \w in|strong="H3027"\w* \w their|strong="H3605"\w* ears, \w and|strong="H3027"\w* \w they|strong="H3027"\w* \w gave|strong="H5414"\w* \w those|strong="H3605"\w* \w rings|strong="H5141"\w* \w to|strong="H5414"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* too. \w And|strong="H3027"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* \w buried|strong="H2934"\w* \w those|strong="H3605"\w* statues \w and|strong="H3027"\w* \w those|strong="H3605"\w* \w rings|strong="H5141"\w* \w under|strong="H8478"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* big tree \w in|strong="H3027"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w place|strong="H8478"\w* called Shekem.   
\p
\v 5 \w Then|strong="H1961"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w his|strong="H5921"\w* mob \w left|strong="H5265"\w* Shekem, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w they|strong="H5921"\w* \w started|strong="H1961"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w go|strong="H1961"\w* towards Bethel. \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* thought \w that|strong="H5892"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w people|strong="H1121"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w towns|strong="H5892"\w* nearby \w might|strong="H1121"\w* attack \w them|strong="H5921"\w*. \w But|strong="H3808"\w* \w God|strong="H3808"\w* looked \w after|strong="H5921"\w* \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w*’s mob. \w God|strong="H3808"\w* \w made|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w people|strong="H1121"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w those|strong="H1121"\w* \w towns|strong="H5892"\w* really frightened, \w so|strong="H1961"\w* \w none|strong="H3808"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* \w them|strong="H5921"\w* attacked \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w*’s mob.   
\p
\v 6 Later \w on|strong="H3605"\w*, \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* \w and|strong="H5971"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* mob got \w to|strong="H5971"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w place|strong="H3605"\w* called \w Bethel|strong="H1008"\w*, \w in|strong="H5971"\w* \w Canaan|strong="H3667"\w* country. \w That|strong="H5971"\w* \w place|strong="H3605"\w* \w used|strong="H3605"\w* \w to|strong="H5971"\w* \w be|strong="H5971"\w* called \w Luz|strong="H3870"\w*.   
\p
