\p \w So|strong="H5414"\w* Judah \w gave|strong="H5414"\w* those things \w to|strong="H5414"\w* Tamar. \w Then|strong="H5414"\w* \w he|strong="H3027"\w* slept \w with|strong="H3027"\w* Tamar, like \w a|strong="H3068"\w* man sleeps \w with|strong="H3027"\w* \w his|strong="H5414"\w* wife, \w and|strong="H3027"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* baby started \w to|strong="H5414"\w* grow \w inside|strong="H3027"\w* \w her|strong="H5414"\w*.\fig Judah gave Tamar his walking stick and the necklace with his special stamp|alt="cropped" src="Gen 38 artist Judith Knowles.tif" size="col" copy="Judith Knowles" ref="38:18" \fig*  
\v 19 \w Then|strong="H6965"\w* Tamar \w left|strong="H5493"\w* \w that|strong="H6965"\w* place, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w she|strong="H5921"\w* \w went|strong="H3212"\w* \w home|strong="H3212"\w*. \w She|strong="H5921"\w* \w took|strong="H5493"\w* \w off|strong="H5493"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* scarf \w that|strong="H6965"\w* was \w over|strong="H5921"\w* \w her|strong="H5921"\w* head, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w she|strong="H5921"\w* \w took|strong="H5493"\w* \w off|strong="H5493"\w* \w those|strong="H5921"\w* pretty \w clothes|strong="H3847"\w*, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w she|strong="H5921"\w* \w put|strong="H3847"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w her|strong="H5921"\w* widow’s \w clothes|strong="H3847"\w* \w again|strong="H6965"\w*.   
\p
