\v 23 \w After|strong="H6779"\w* \w that|strong="H2009"\w*, another 7 groups \w of|strong="H7641"\w* seeds started \w to|strong="H6921"\w* \w grow|strong="H6779"\w*. They \w were|strong="H2009"\w* \w small|strong="H1851"\w* \w and|strong="H7651"\w* dry, because \w a|strong="H3068"\w* hot dry \w wind|strong="H6921"\w* blew on them.  
\v 24 Then those 7 groups \w of|strong="H2748"\w* \w small|strong="H1851"\w* dry seeds, they ate \w the|strong="H5046"\w* 7 groups \w of|strong="H2748"\w* \w good|strong="H2896"\w* big seeds, \w like|strong="H2896"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* person eats food. \w That|strong="H2896"\w* \w was|strong="H2896"\w* \w the|strong="H5046"\w* \w end|strong="H1104"\w* \w of|strong="H2748"\w* \w my|strong="H5046"\w* dream.”  
\p Then Pharaoh said \w to|strong="H5046"\w* Joseph, “\w I|strong="H5046"\w* talked \w to|strong="H5046"\w* \w the|strong="H5046"\w* \w men|strong="H7651"\w* \w that|strong="H2896"\w* can do magic, \w and|strong="H2896"\w* \w I|strong="H5046"\w* \w told|strong="H5046"\w* \w them|strong="H5046"\w* about those dreams \w that|strong="H2896"\w* \w I|strong="H5046"\w* had. \w But|strong="H1104"\w* they don’t \w know|strong="H5046"\w* \w what|strong="H2896"\w* \w my|strong="H5046"\w* dreams mean.”   
\p
