\v 30 \w But|strong="H7911"\w* \w after|strong="H6965"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w*, \w there|strong="H6965"\w* \w will|strong="H4714"\w* \w be|strong="H8141"\w* 7 dry \w years|strong="H8141"\w*. \w There|strong="H6965"\w* \w will|strong="H4714"\w* \w be|strong="H8141"\w* \w no|strong="H3605"\w* rain \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w no|strong="H3605"\w* food plants growing \w anywhere|strong="H3605"\w* \w in|strong="H8141"\w* \w Egypt|strong="H4714"\w*. \w Those|strong="H3605"\w* dry \w years|strong="H8141"\w* \w will|strong="H4714"\w* \w be|strong="H8141"\w* bad \w for|strong="H4714"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w whole|strong="H3605"\w* country. \w All|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* people \w in|strong="H8141"\w* \w Egypt|strong="H4714"\w*, \w they|strong="H8141"\w* \w will|strong="H4714"\w* \w forget|strong="H7911"\w* \w about|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w time|strong="H8141"\w* \w when|strong="H3615"\w* \w there|strong="H6965"\w* \w was|strong="H8141"\w* lots \w and|strong="H6965"\w* lots \w of|strong="H8141"\w* food.  
\v 31 \w Those|strong="H1931"\w* dry years \w will|strong="H3808"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* \w so|strong="H3651"\w* bad, \w it|strong="H1931"\w* \w will|strong="H3808"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* just \w like|strong="H3651"\w* \w those|strong="H1931"\w* 7 \w good|strong="H3966"\w* years \w never|strong="H3808"\w* happened.  
\v 32 Sir, God \w is|strong="H1697"\w* going \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w make|strong="H6213"\w* \w those|strong="H5921"\w* \w things|strong="H1697"\w* \w happen|strong="H1697"\w*, \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w sure|strong="H3559"\w*. \w And|strong="H6213"\w* \w he|strong="H3588"\w*’s going \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w make|strong="H6213"\w* \w them|strong="H5921"\w* \w happen|strong="H1697"\w* \w soon|strong="H4116"\w*. \w That|strong="H3588"\w*’s \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w reason|strong="H1697"\w* \w why|strong="H5921"\w* \w he|strong="H3588"\w* \w gave|strong="H6213"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* 2 \w dreams|strong="H2472"\w* \w about|strong="H5921"\w* \w them|strong="H5921"\w*.”   
\p
\v 33 \w Then|strong="H6258"\w* Joseph said, “Sir, \w now|strong="H6258"\w* \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w will|strong="H4714"\w* \w tell|strong="H7200"\w* \w you|strong="H5921"\w* \w what|strong="H7200"\w* \w you|strong="H5921"\w* \w have|strong="H7200"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* do. \w You|strong="H5921"\w* \w have|strong="H7200"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w pick|strong="H7200"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w man|strong="H2450"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w is|strong="H4714"\w* really \w wise|strong="H2450"\w* \w and|strong="H4714"\w* thinks properly. \w And|strong="H4714"\w* \w you|strong="H5921"\w* \w have|strong="H7200"\w* \w to|strong="H5921"\w* \w put|strong="H7896"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w man|strong="H2450"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w charge|strong="H5921"\w* \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \w Egypt|strong="H4714"\w* country.  
\v 34-35 Then you have to pick some other men to work for him. And those men have to go all over Egypt country, and they have to gather up food from all the farms. Every time the farmers have food plants with seeds that are ready to make flour, those workers have to say to the farmers, ‘This is what Pharaoh says you have to do. Split up that food into 5 piles, and give one pile to us.’ Then those workers have to put that food in big sheds in the towns, and they have to look after it. They have to keep on doing that for 7 years, while there is lots and lots of food in Egypt country.  
\v 36 \w At|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H3772"\w* end \w of|strong="H8141"\w* \w those|strong="H1961"\w* 7 good \w years|strong="H8141"\w*, \w there|strong="H1961"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* 7 dry \w years|strong="H8141"\w*. \w There|strong="H1961"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* \w no|strong="H3808"\w* rain, \w and|strong="H4714"\w* \w no|strong="H3808"\w* food plants \w will|strong="H1961"\w* grow \w in|strong="H8141"\w* \w Egypt|strong="H4714"\w* country. \w But|strong="H3808"\w* \w all|strong="H3772"\w* \w the|strong="H3772"\w* \w people|strong="H3808"\w* \w in|strong="H8141"\w* \w Egypt|strong="H4714"\w* country, \w they|strong="H3808"\w* \w can|strong="H3808"\w* eat \w the|strong="H3772"\w* food \w that|strong="H8141"\w* \w is|strong="H1961"\w* \w in|strong="H8141"\w* \w those|strong="H1961"\w* sheds, \w and|strong="H4714"\w* \w they|strong="H3808"\w* \w can|strong="H3808"\w* \w keep|strong="H1961"\w* \w on|strong="H1961"\w* doing \w that|strong="H8141"\w* \w for|strong="H4714"\w* \w those|strong="H1961"\w* 7 dry \w years|strong="H8141"\w*, \w so|strong="H1961"\w* \w that|strong="H8141"\w* \w they|strong="H3808"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* die.”   
\s1 Pharaoh put Joseph in charge of Egypt country  
\p
\v 37 \w Pharaoh|strong="H6547"\w* \w and|strong="H5869"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* workers listened \w to|strong="H1697"\w* Joseph, \w and|strong="H5869"\w* \w they|strong="H1697"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w liked|strong="H5869"\w* Joseph’s \w idea|strong="H1697"\w*.  
