\s1 Joseph’s brothers went to Egypt country again  
\p
\v 15 Straight \w away|strong="H3947"\w*, Jacob’s sons \w did|strong="H1144"\w* everything \w that|strong="H3027"\w* Jacob said. \w They|strong="H6440"\w* \w got|strong="H6965"\w* \w those|strong="H2063"\w* \w presents|strong="H4503"\w* ready, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w they|strong="H6440"\w* \w got|strong="H6965"\w* \w that|strong="H3027"\w* \w money|strong="H3701"\w* \w that|strong="H3027"\w* \w they|strong="H6440"\w* found \w in|strong="H6440"\w* \w their|strong="H3947"\w* food bags, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w some|strong="H3027"\w* \w other|strong="H2063"\w* \w money|strong="H3701"\w*. \w Then|strong="H6965"\w* \w they|strong="H6440"\w* \w got|strong="H6965"\w* \w their|strong="H3947"\w* brother \w Benjamin|strong="H1144"\w*, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w they|strong="H6440"\w* \w went|strong="H3381"\w* \w to|strong="H3381"\w* \w Egypt|strong="H4714"\w* country. \w After|strong="H6965"\w* \w they|strong="H6440"\w* \w got|strong="H6965"\w* \w there|strong="H5975"\w*, \w they|strong="H6440"\w* \w went|strong="H3381"\w* \w and|strong="H6965"\w* \w stood|strong="H5975"\w* \w in|strong="H6440"\w* \w front|strong="H6440"\w* \w of|strong="H3027"\w* \w Joseph|strong="H3130"\w*.   
