\v 13 \w Then|strong="H7725"\w* \w all|strong="H5921"\w* \w those|strong="H5921"\w* men got \w a|strong="H3068"\w* big shock, \w and|strong="H7725"\w* \w they|strong="H5921"\w* thought, “\w Now|strong="H5921"\w* Benjamin \w will|strong="H5892"\w* \w have|strong="H5892"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* stay \w in|strong="H5921"\w* Egypt country \w and|strong="H7725"\w* work \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w that|strong="H5892"\w* man.” \w So|strong="H7725"\w* \w they|strong="H5921"\w* got \w really|strong="H7725"\w* upset. \w They|strong="H5921"\w* \w were|strong="H5892"\w* \w so|strong="H7725"\w* upset \w that|strong="H5892"\w* \w they|strong="H5921"\w* \w tore|strong="H7167"\w* \w their|strong="H7725"\w* \w clothes|strong="H8071"\w*. \w Then|strong="H7725"\w* \w they|strong="H5921"\w* \w put|strong="H7725"\w* \w their|strong="H7725"\w* bags \w back|strong="H7725"\w* \w on|strong="H5921"\w* \w their|strong="H7725"\w* \w donkeys|strong="H2543"\w*, \w and|strong="H7725"\w* \w they|strong="H5921"\w* \w went|strong="H7725"\w* \w back|strong="H7725"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w town|strong="H5892"\w* \w where|strong="H5921"\w* \w Joseph|strong="H7725"\w* lived.   
\s1 Judah tried to save Benjamin  
\p
\v 14 \w Joseph|strong="H3130"\w* \w was|strong="H1931"\w* \w in|strong="H1004"\w* \w his|strong="H6440"\w* \w house|strong="H1004"\w*, \w and|strong="H3063"\w* \w he|strong="H1931"\w* \w was|strong="H1931"\w* waiting \w for|strong="H6440"\w* \w those|strong="H1931"\w* men \w to|strong="H6440"\w* \w come|strong="H5307"\w* \w back|strong="H5750"\w*. \w Then|strong="H5307"\w* \w those|strong="H1931"\w* men got \w to|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w house|strong="H1004"\w*. \w The|strong="H6440"\w* \w one|strong="H1931"\w* \w called|strong="H8033"\w* \w Judah|strong="H3063"\w*, \w he|strong="H1931"\w* \w went|strong="H3063"\w* \w inside|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w house|strong="H1004"\w*, \w and|strong="H3063"\w* \w his|strong="H6440"\w* brothers \w went|strong="H3063"\w* \w inside|strong="H1004"\w* \w too|strong="H5750"\w*. \w You|strong="H6440"\w* know, \w all|strong="H5750"\w* \w those|strong="H1931"\w* men \w were|strong="H3063"\w* \w Joseph|strong="H3130"\w*’s brothers, \w but|strong="H1931"\w* \w they|strong="H8033"\w* \w still|strong="H5750"\w* didn’t know \w that|strong="H1931"\w* \w he|strong="H1931"\w* \w was|strong="H1931"\w* \w Joseph|strong="H3130"\w*. \w So|strong="H1931"\w* \w they|strong="H8033"\w* quickly got \w down|strong="H5307"\w* \w on|strong="H5307"\w* \w their|strong="H6440"\w* knees \w and|strong="H3063"\w* put \w their|strong="H6440"\w* \w faces|strong="H6440"\w* \w near|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w ground|strong="H6440"\w*, \w to|strong="H6440"\w* show \w him|strong="H6440"\w* \w respect|strong="H6440"\w*.   
\p
\v 15 \w Joseph|strong="H3130"\w* \w still|strong="H3588"\w* wanted \w to|strong="H6213"\w* trick \w them|strong="H6213"\w*, \w so|strong="H6213"\w* \w he|strong="H3588"\w* said \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w them|strong="H6213"\w*, “\w You|strong="H3588"\w* \w know|strong="H3045"\w*, \w I|strong="H3588"\w*’m \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w very|strong="H2088"\w* powerful \w man|strong="H2088"\w*. \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w can|strong="H4100"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* magic \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w find|strong="H3045"\w* \w out|strong="H6213"\w* \w things|strong="H4639"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w nobody|strong="H3808"\w* \w else|strong="H3808"\w* \w knows|strong="H3045"\w*. \w So|strong="H6213"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w know|strong="H3045"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* mob stole \w my|strong="H3045"\w* silver cup. \w Why|strong="H4100"\w* \w did|strong="H6213"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* bad \w thing|strong="H2088"\w*?”   
\p
\v 16 \w Judah|strong="H3063"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w Joseph|strong="H3027"\w*, “Sir, \w we|strong="H3068"\w* don’t know \w what|strong="H4100"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w say|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w you|strong="H4100"\w*. \w We|strong="H2005"\w* really don’t know \w what|strong="H4100"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w say|strong="H1696"\w*. \w We|strong="H2005"\w* didn’t steal \w your|strong="H3027"\w* \w cup|strong="H1375"\w*. \w That|strong="H3027"\w*’s \w the|strong="H3027"\w* true story, \w but|strong="H1696"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* don’t \w have|strong="H1571"\w* \w any|strong="H1571"\w* way \w to|strong="H1696"\w* show \w you|strong="H4100"\w* \w that|strong="H3027"\w* \w it|strong="H1696"\w*’s true.”\fig Judah told Joseph that they didn’t steal that cup|alt="Cropped. Could go further down." src="KV-017.tif" size="col" copy="Voigtlander" ref="44:16" \fig*  
\p \w Then|strong="H1696"\w* \w Judah|strong="H3063"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w Joseph|strong="H3027"\w*, “Sir, \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w long|strong="H4100"\w* time ago, \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w did|strong="H4100"\w* bad things, \w and|strong="H3063"\w* \w God|strong="H3027"\w* knows \w that|strong="H3027"\w*. \w Now|strong="H1571"\w* \w God|strong="H3027"\w* \w is|strong="H4100"\w* showing \w you|strong="H4100"\w* \w that|strong="H3027"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w are|strong="H3027"\w* \w guilty|strong="H5771"\w* \w men|strong="H5650"\w*. \w So|strong="H1571"\w* \w listen|strong="H2005"\w*, \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H5650"\w* \w all|strong="H4672"\w* \w become|strong="H3027"\w* \w your|strong="H3027"\w* work-men. \w Yes|strong="H1571"\w*, \w that|strong="H3027"\w* man \w that|strong="H3027"\w* \w had|strong="H3063"\w* \w your|strong="H3027"\w* \w cup|strong="H1375"\w* \w in|strong="H1696"\w* \w his|strong="H3027"\w* bag, \w he|strong="H3027"\w* \w will|strong="H5650"\w* \w become|strong="H3027"\w* \w your|strong="H3027"\w* work-man, \w and|strong="H3063"\w* \w the|strong="H3027"\w* rest \w of|strong="H3027"\w* \w us|strong="H3027"\w* mob, \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H5650"\w* \w become|strong="H3027"\w* \w your|strong="H3027"\w* work-men \w too|strong="H1571"\w*. \w And|strong="H3063"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H5650"\w* \w work|strong="H3027"\w* \w for|strong="H3027"\w* \w you|strong="H4100"\w* \w for|strong="H3027"\w* \w no|strong="H4672"\w* pay.”   
\p
\v 17 \w But|strong="H1961"\w* \w Joseph|strong="H3027"\w* said, “\w No|strong="H6213"\w* \w way|strong="H2063"\w*. \w I|strong="H5650"\w* don’t want \w to|strong="H5927"\w* \w punish|strong="H6213"\w* \w all|strong="H6213"\w* \w of|strong="H3027"\w* \w you|strong="H6213"\w* \w like|strong="H1961"\w* \w that|strong="H1931"\w*. \w The|strong="H6213"\w* man \w that|strong="H1931"\w* \w had|strong="H1961"\w* \w my|strong="H1961"\w* \w cup|strong="H1375"\w* \w in|strong="H6213"\w* \w his|strong="H3027"\w* bag, \w he|strong="H1931"\w* \w is|strong="H1931"\w* \w the|strong="H6213"\w* \w only|strong="H7965"\w* \w one|strong="H1931"\w* \w that|strong="H1931"\w* \w has|strong="H1961"\w* \w to|strong="H5927"\w* \w become|strong="H1961"\w* \w my|strong="H1961"\w* work-man. \w The|strong="H6213"\w* \w rest|strong="H7965"\w* \w of|strong="H3027"\w* \w you|strong="H6213"\w* mob, \w you|strong="H6213"\w* \w can|strong="H5650"\w* \w go|strong="H5927"\w* home \w to|strong="H5927"\w* \w your|strong="H6213"\w* father, \w and|strong="H3027"\w* \w I|strong="H5650"\w* \w will|strong="H1961"\w* \w not|strong="H6213"\w* \w make|strong="H6213"\w* \w any|strong="H6213"\w* trouble \w for|strong="H6213"\w* \w you|strong="H6213"\w*.”   
\p
\v 18 \w Then|strong="H1696"\w* \w Judah|strong="H3063"\w* \w went|strong="H3063"\w* \w more|strong="H3588"\w* \w close|strong="H5066"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* Joseph, \w and|strong="H3063"\w* \w Judah|strong="H3063"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w*, “Sir, \w please|strong="H4994"\w* \w let|strong="H4994"\w* \w me|strong="H4994"\w* \w say|strong="H1696"\w* \w something|strong="H1697"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w*, \w even|strong="H3588"\w* \w though|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* am \w not|strong="H1696"\w* \w an|strong="H3588"\w* important \w person|strong="H1696"\w*. \w I|strong="H3588"\w* know \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w are|strong="H1697"\w* \w very|strong="H2734"\w* important, \w just|strong="H1697"\w* \w like|strong="H3644"\w* \w Pharaoh|strong="H6547"\w*, \w the|strong="H3588"\w* big boss \w of|strong="H1697"\w* Egypt country. \w So|strong="H5066"\w* \w please|strong="H4994"\w* don’t \w be|strong="H1697"\w* \w angry|strong="H2734"\w* \w with|strong="H1696"\w* \w me|strong="H4994"\w* \w for|strong="H3588"\w* \w saying|strong="H1697"\w* \w this|strong="H1696"\w*.  
\v 19 \w You|strong="H7592"\w* know, sir, \w the|strong="H5650"\w* last time \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w came|strong="H5650"\w* \w here|strong="H3426"\w*, \w you|strong="H7592"\w* \w asked|strong="H7592"\w* \w us|strong="H7592"\w*, ‘\w Is|strong="H3426"\w* \w your|strong="H7592"\w* father still alive? \w And|strong="H5650"\w* \w do|strong="H3426"\w* \w you|strong="H7592"\w* \w have|strong="H3426"\w* \w another|strong="H3426"\w* brother?’  
\v 20 \w Then|strong="H3426"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* said \w to|strong="H4191"\w* \w you|strong="H3426"\w*, ‘Yes, sir. \w Our|strong="H3426"\w* father \w is|strong="H3426"\w* alive, \w and|strong="H2205"\w* \w he|strong="H1931"\w* \w is|strong="H3426"\w* \w an|strong="H3426"\w* \w old|strong="H2205"\w* \w man|strong="H2205"\w*. \w And|strong="H2205"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w have|strong="H3426"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w young|strong="H3206"\w* brother too. \w He|strong="H1931"\w* \w was|strong="H1931"\w* born when \w our|strong="H3426"\w* father \w was|strong="H1931"\w* already \w old|strong="H2205"\w*. \w We|strong="H4191"\w* \w had|strong="H3426"\w* \w one|strong="H1931"\w* \w more|strong="H3498"\w* brother, \w but|strong="H3498"\w* \w he|strong="H1931"\w* \w died|strong="H4191"\w*. \w That|strong="H1931"\w* brother \w that|strong="H1931"\w* \w died|strong="H4191"\w*, \w and|strong="H2205"\w* \w our|strong="H3426"\w* \w young|strong="H3206"\w* brother, \w they|strong="H1931"\w* \w had|strong="H3426"\w* \w the|strong="H4191"\w* \w same|strong="H1931"\w* mother. \w So|strong="H4191"\w* now \w our|strong="H3426"\w* \w young|strong="H3206"\w* brother \w is|strong="H3426"\w* \w the|strong="H4191"\w* only kid \w left|strong="H3498"\w* \w from|strong="H4191"\w* \w his|strong="H4191"\w* mother. \w And|strong="H2205"\w* \w our|strong="H3426"\w* father really loves \w him|strong="H4191"\w*.’  
\v 21 \w Then|strong="H7760"\w* \w you|strong="H5921"\w* said \w to|strong="H3381"\w* \w us|strong="H5921"\w*, ‘\w Go|strong="H3381"\w* \w and|strong="H5869"\w* \w get|strong="H7760"\w* \w that|strong="H5650"\w* young man, \w and|strong="H5869"\w* \w bring|strong="H3381"\w* \w him|strong="H5921"\w* \w here|strong="H7760"\w* \w to|strong="H3381"\w* Egypt country, \w so|strong="H7760"\w* \w that|strong="H5650"\w* \w I|strong="H5921"\w* \w can|strong="H5650"\w* \w see|strong="H5869"\w* \w him|strong="H5921"\w*.’  
\v 22 \w But|strong="H3808"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* said, ‘Sir, \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w can|strong="H3201"\w*’t take \w that|strong="H5288"\w* \w young|strong="H5288"\w* \w man|strong="H5288"\w* away \w from|strong="H4191"\w* \w his|strong="H5800"\w* father. If \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w do|strong="H3201"\w* \w that|strong="H5288"\w*, \w his|strong="H5800"\w* father \w will|strong="H3808"\w* \w be|strong="H4191"\w* \w so|strong="H3808"\w* sad \w that|strong="H5288"\w* \w he|strong="H3808"\w* \w will|strong="H3808"\w* \w die|strong="H4191"\w*.’  
\v 23 \w Then|strong="H3254"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* said \w to|strong="H3381"\w* \w us|strong="H6440"\w*, ‘\w You|strong="H6440"\w* mob \w can|strong="H3254"\w* only \w come|strong="H3381"\w* back here \w if|strong="H7200"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w bring|strong="H3381"\w* \w your|strong="H6440"\w* \w youngest|strong="H6996"\w* brother \w with|strong="H3381"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w*.’”   
\p
\v 24 Judah \w kept|strong="H1961"\w* \w on|strong="H1961"\w* \w talking|strong="H1697"\w* \w to|strong="H5927"\w* Joseph. \w He|strong="H3588"\w* \w said|strong="H1697"\w*, “Sir, \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w went|strong="H5927"\w* \w back|strong="H5927"\w* home \w to|strong="H5927"\w* \w our|strong="H1961"\w* father, \w and|strong="H5650"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w told|strong="H5046"\w* \w him|strong="H5046"\w* \w those|strong="H1961"\w* \w things|strong="H1697"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w said|strong="H1697"\w*.  
\v 25 \w Then|strong="H7725"\w*, \w some|strong="H4592"\w* time later, \w our|strong="H7725"\w* father said \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w us|strong="H7725"\w*, ‘\w Go|strong="H7725"\w* \w back|strong="H7725"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* Egypt, \w and|strong="H7725"\w* \w buy|strong="H7666"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* bit \w more|strong="H7725"\w* food \w for|strong="H7725"\w* \w us|strong="H7725"\w* mob.’  
\v 26 \w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* said \w to|strong="H3381"\w* \w him|strong="H6440"\w*, ‘\w That|strong="H3588"\w* \w man|strong="H7200"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w is|strong="H3426"\w* \w in|strong="H6440"\w* charge \w of|strong="H6440"\w* Egypt, \w he|strong="H3588"\w* said \w to|strong="H3381"\w* \w us|strong="H6440"\w*, “\w You|strong="H3588"\w* mob \w can|strong="H3201"\w* \w only|strong="H3588"\w* \w come|strong="H3381"\w* back \w here|strong="H3426"\w* \w if|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w bring|strong="H3381"\w* \w your|strong="H6440"\w* \w youngest|strong="H6996"\w* brother \w with|strong="H6440"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w*.” ’ \w So|strong="H3808"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* said \w to|strong="H3381"\w* \w our|strong="H7200"\w* father, ‘\w If|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H3808"\w* \w let|strong="H3381"\w* \w our|strong="H7200"\w* \w youngest|strong="H6996"\w* brother \w go|strong="H3381"\w* \w with|strong="H6440"\w* \w us|strong="H6440"\w* \w to|strong="H3381"\w* Egypt, \w then|strong="H3588"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3808"\w* \w go|strong="H3381"\w*. \w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w if|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* don’t \w let|strong="H3381"\w* \w him|strong="H6440"\w* \w go|strong="H3381"\w* \w with|strong="H6440"\w* \w us|strong="H6440"\w*, \w then|strong="H3588"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w can|strong="H3201"\w*’t \w go|strong="H3381"\w*.’  
\v 27 \w Then|strong="H3588"\w* \w my|strong="H3045"\w* \w father|strong="H3205"\w* said \w to|strong="H3205"\w* \w us|strong="H3045"\w*, ‘Listen, \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w know|strong="H3045"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* really loved \w my|strong="H3045"\w* wife Rachel, \w and|strong="H5650"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w only|strong="H3588"\w* \w had|strong="H3205"\w* 2 \w sons|strong="H3205"\w* \w together|strong="H8147"\w*.  
\v 28 \w One|strong="H3808"\w* \w of|strong="H3318"\w* \w those|strong="H3318"\w* sons \w went|strong="H3318"\w* \w away|strong="H3318"\w*, \w and|strong="H7200"\w* \w he|strong="H5704"\w* \w never|strong="H3808"\w* \w came|strong="H3318"\w* \w back|strong="H3318"\w*. \w So|strong="H3808"\w* \w I|strong="H5704"\w* \w said|strong="H3318"\w*, “\w I|strong="H5704"\w* know \w what|strong="H7200"\w* happened. \w A|strong="H3068"\w* wild animal \w tore|strong="H2963"\w* \w my|strong="H7200"\w* son \w into|strong="H3318"\w* \w little|strong="H5704"\w* bits.” \w And|strong="H7200"\w* \w I|strong="H5704"\w* \w never|strong="H3808"\w* \w saw|strong="H7200"\w* \w him|strong="H7200"\w* again.  
\v 29 \w So|strong="H3947"\w* \w now|strong="H1571"\w* \w your|strong="H3947"\w* youngest brother, \w he|strong="H6440"\w* \w is|strong="H2088"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w only|strong="H1571"\w* \w one|strong="H2088"\w* \w of|strong="H6440"\w* Rachel’s sons \w that|strong="H2088"\w* \w I|strong="H2088"\w* \w have|strong="H1571"\w* \w left|strong="H3381"\w*. If \w you|strong="H6440"\w* \w take|strong="H3947"\w* \w him|strong="H6440"\w* \w away|strong="H3947"\w* \w from|strong="H6440"\w* \w me|strong="H6440"\w*, \w he|strong="H6440"\w* might \w get|strong="H3947"\w* \w hurt|strong="H7451"\w*, \w or|strong="H1571"\w* \w he|strong="H6440"\w* might die. \w You|strong="H6440"\w* know, \w I|strong="H2088"\w* am \w an|strong="H3947"\w* \w old|strong="H7872"\w* \w man|strong="H7451"\w*. If something \w bad|strong="H7451"\w* \w happens|strong="H7136"\w* \w to|strong="H3381"\w* \w my|strong="H3947"\w* son, \w I|strong="H2088"\w* \w will|strong="H1571"\w* \w be|strong="H1571"\w* \w so|strong="H3947"\w* \w sad|strong="H7451"\w* \w that|strong="H2088"\w* \w I|strong="H2088"\w* \w will|strong="H1571"\w* die.’”   
\p
\v 30-31 Judah kept on talking to Joseph. He said, “Sir, our father really loves that young man. He loves him more than anything else. And you know, our father is very old. I’m telling you, if I go back home to my father, and if that young man is not with us, then my father will be so sad that he will die. Yes, as soon as he sees that the young man is not with us, he will die straight away. We don’t want to do that to our father.  
\v 32 Sir, \w I|strong="H3588"\w* promised \w my|strong="H3605"\w* father \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H5650"\w* look \w after|strong="H3117"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w young|strong="H5288"\w* \w man|strong="H5288"\w*, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* keep \w him|strong="H5973"\w* safe. \w I|strong="H3588"\w* said \w to|strong="H3117"\w* \w my|strong="H3605"\w* father, ‘\w If|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* don’t \w bring|strong="H2398"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w young|strong="H5288"\w* \w man|strong="H5288"\w* back here \w to|strong="H3117"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w*, \w then|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w can|strong="H5650"\w* \w blame|strong="H2398"\w* \w me|strong="H5973"\w* \w and|strong="H3117"\w* say \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w I|strong="H3588"\w* am guilty, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w can|strong="H5650"\w* \w do|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w my|strong="H3605"\w* \w life|strong="H3117"\w*.’  
