\c 48  
\s1 Jacob was good to Joseph’s sons  
\p
\v 1 \w One|strong="H1121"\w* day, \w not|strong="H1961"\w* long \w after|strong="H1961"\w* \w that|strong="H1697"\w*, somebody \w said|strong="H1697"\w* \w to|strong="H1961"\w* \w Joseph|strong="H3130"\w*, “\w Your|strong="H3947"\w* \w father|strong="H1121"\w* \w is|strong="H1697"\w* really \w sick|strong="H2470"\w*. \w He|strong="H8147"\w* \w might|strong="H1121"\w* \w die|strong="H1121"\w* soon.”  
