\p
\v 28 \w In|strong="H3478"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w way|strong="H2063"\w*, Jacob \w talked|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* 12 sons, \w and|strong="H3478"\w* \w he|strong="H3605"\w* \w told|strong="H1696"\w* \w them|strong="H8147"\w* \w about|strong="H3605"\w* \w things|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w will|strong="H3478"\w* happen \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w them|strong="H8147"\w* \w and|strong="H3478"\w* \w their|strong="H3605"\w* families later \w on|strong="H1696"\w*. \w He|strong="H3605"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w* different \w things|strong="H3605"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w each|strong="H3605"\w* \w of|strong="H7626"\w* \w his|strong="H3605"\w* sons, \w and|strong="H3478"\w* \w those|strong="H3605"\w* \w things|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w he|strong="H3605"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \w were|strong="H3478"\w* \w right|strong="H3478"\w* \w for|strong="H3478"\w* \w each|strong="H3605"\w* \w one|strong="H3605"\w* \w of|strong="H7626"\w* \w them|strong="H8147"\w*.  
\p \w You|strong="H3605"\w* know, later \w on|strong="H1696"\w*, Jacob’s 12 sons became \w the|strong="H3605"\w* grand-fathers \w of|strong="H7626"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* 12 \w tribes|strong="H7626"\w* \w in|strong="H3478"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w Israel|strong="H3478"\w* mob.   
\s1 Jacob told his sons to bury his body in a cave  
\p
\v 29-30 Then Jacob said to his sons, “I am going to die very soon. After I die, I want you mob to bury my body in that cave in Canaan country. My father’s body and my grand-father’s body are already in that cave. That cave is on some land in the place called Makpelah, to the east of Mamreh, in Canaan country. That land used to belong to \w a|strong="H3068"\w* man from the Heth tribe, called Efron. My grand-father Abraham, he bought that land from Efron, to use as \w a|strong="H3068"\w* grave.\x * \xo 49:29-30 \xt Genesis 23:3-20\x*  
\v 31 \w And|strong="H8033"\w* Abraham \w buried|strong="H6912"\w* \w his|strong="H3327"\w* wife \w Sarah|strong="H8283"\w* \w there|strong="H8033"\w*. \w Some|strong="H8033"\w* time later, Abraham died, \w and|strong="H8033"\w* \w they|strong="H8033"\w* \w buried|strong="H6912"\w* \w him|strong="H6912"\w* \w in|strong="H6912"\w* \w that|strong="H8033"\w* same \w place|strong="H8033"\w*. \w My|strong="H6912"\w* father \w Isaac|strong="H3327"\w* \w and|strong="H8033"\w* \w his|strong="H3327"\w* wife \w Rebekah|strong="H7259"\w*, \w they|strong="H8033"\w* \w are|strong="H8033"\w* \w buried|strong="H6912"\w* \w there|strong="H8033"\w* too. \w And|strong="H8033"\w* \w I|strong="H8033"\w* also \w buried|strong="H6912"\w* \w my|strong="H6912"\w* wife \w Leah|strong="H3812"\w* \w there|strong="H8033"\w*.\x * \xo 49:31 \xt Genesis 25:9-10; 35:29\x*  
\v 32 \w That|strong="H1121"\w* \w land|strong="H7704"\w* \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w that|strong="H1121"\w* \w cave|strong="H4631"\w*, they used \w to|strong="H1121"\w* belong \w to|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H1121"\w* \w Heth|strong="H2845"\w* \w people|strong="H1121"\w*, but now \w that|strong="H1121"\w* place belongs \w to|strong="H1121"\w* our family.”   
\p
\v 33 \w Jacob|strong="H3290"\w* \w finished|strong="H3615"\w* saying \w all|strong="H3615"\w* \w those|strong="H1121"\w* things \w to|strong="H1121"\w* \w his|strong="H6680"\w* \w sons|strong="H1121"\w*, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w he|strong="H7272"\w* \w lay|strong="H1121"\w* \w down|strong="H6680"\w* \w on|strong="H3615"\w* \w his|strong="H6680"\w* \w bed|strong="H4296"\w*. \w Then|strong="H6680"\w* \w he|strong="H7272"\w* \w breathed|strong="H1478"\w* \w for|strong="H1121"\w* \w the|strong="H6680"\w* \w last|strong="H1478"\w* time, \w and|strong="H1121"\w* \w he|strong="H7272"\w* \w died|strong="H1478"\w*.\x * \xo 49:33 \xt Acts 7:15\x*   
\c 50  
\s1 Joseph had a big funeral for his father  
\p
\v 1 \w Then|strong="H5307"\w* \w Joseph|strong="H3130"\w* bent \w down|strong="H5307"\w* \w and|strong="H6440"\w* \w hugged|strong="H5307"\w* \w his|strong="H6440"\w* father’s body. \w He|strong="H5921"\w* \w cried|strong="H1058"\w*, \w and|strong="H6440"\w* \w he|strong="H5921"\w* \w kissed|strong="H5401"\w* \w his|strong="H6440"\w* father’s \w face|strong="H6440"\w*.  
\v 2 \w Then|strong="H6680"\w* \w Joseph|strong="H3130"\w* talked \w to|strong="H3478"\w* some \w of|strong="H5650"\w* \w his|strong="H6680"\w* workers. \w Joseph|strong="H3130"\w* said \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w them|strong="H6680"\w*, “\w My|strong="H5650"\w* father Jacob died. \w Now|strong="H3478"\w* \w I|strong="H6680"\w* want \w you|strong="H6680"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* get \w his|strong="H6680"\w* body ready \w for|strong="H5650"\w* \w the|strong="H6680"\w* funeral. \w I|strong="H6680"\w* want \w you|strong="H6680"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* look after \w his|strong="H6680"\w* body \w in|strong="H3478"\w* \w that|strong="H3478"\w* special way \w that|strong="H3478"\w* \w you|strong="H6680"\w* \w do|strong="H6680"\w* \w for|strong="H5650"\w* important people.”  
\p \w So|strong="H6680"\w* those \w men|strong="H5650"\w* worked \w on|strong="H5650"\w* Jacob’s body \w to|strong="H3478"\w* get \w it|strong="H6680"\w* ready, \w then|strong="H6680"\w* \w they|strong="H3478"\w* \w put|strong="H6680"\w* special oils \w and|strong="H3478"\w* perfumes \w on|strong="H5650"\w* \w his|strong="H6680"\w* body, \w so|strong="H6680"\w* \w that|strong="H3478"\w* \w it|strong="H6680"\w* \w will|strong="H3478"\w* not rot away. \w Then|strong="H6680"\w* \w they|strong="H3478"\w* wrapped \w his|strong="H6680"\w* body \w in|strong="H3478"\w* long bits \w of|strong="H5650"\w* cloth, \w and|strong="H3478"\w* \w they|strong="H3478"\w* \w put|strong="H6680"\w* \w it|strong="H6680"\w* \w in|strong="H3478"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* special coffin.\fig Some Egypt people put special oils on Jacob’s body and wrapped it in long bits of cloth|alt="(BING AI image creator)" src="Bing mummification.jpg" size="col" copy="N/A (AI)" ref="50:2" \fig*  
\v 3 \w It|strong="H3588"\w* \w took|strong="H4390"\w* \w them|strong="H3117"\w* 40 \w days|strong="H3117"\w* \w to|strong="H3117"\w* finish doing \w all|strong="H1058"\w* \w those|strong="H3588"\w* things.  
\p \w The|strong="H3588"\w* \w Egypt|strong="H4713"\w* people \w cried|strong="H1058"\w* \w for|strong="H3588"\w* Jacob \w for|strong="H3588"\w* 70 \w days|strong="H3117"\w*.   
\p
\v 4 \w At|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H3117"\w* end \w of|strong="H1004"\w* \w those|strong="H1696"\w* 70 \w days|strong="H3117"\w*, \w Joseph|strong="H3130"\w* \w talked|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w Pharaoh|strong="H6547"\w*’s important workers. \w Joseph|strong="H3130"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w them|strong="H5674"\w*, “\w I|strong="H3117"\w* want \w you|strong="H3117"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w do|strong="H5869"\w* something \w for|strong="H1004"\w* \w me|strong="H4994"\w*. \w Please|strong="H4994"\w* \w be|strong="H3117"\w* \w good|strong="H5869"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w me|strong="H4994"\w*, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \w do|strong="H5869"\w* \w this|strong="H1696"\w* \w thing|strong="H4994"\w* \w that|strong="H3117"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* ask. \w Please|strong="H4994"\w* \w go|strong="H5674"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w Pharaoh|strong="H6547"\w*, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \w tell|strong="H1696"\w* \w him|strong="H4672"\w* \w that|strong="H3117"\w* \w I|strong="H3117"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w*,  
\v 5 ‘\w My|strong="H7725"\w* father talked \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w me|strong="H4994"\w* before \w he|strong="H8033"\w* \w died|strong="H4191"\w*. \w He|strong="H8033"\w* said, “\w I|strong="H2009"\w* am \w going|strong="H5927"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w die|strong="H4191"\w* \w very|strong="H6258"\w* \w soon|strong="H6258"\w*. \w After|strong="H5927"\w* \w I|strong="H2009"\w* \w die|strong="H4191"\w*, \w I|strong="H2009"\w* want \w you|strong="H7725"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w take|strong="H7725"\w* \w my|strong="H7725"\w* \w body|strong="H4191"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w Canaan|strong="H3667"\w* country, \w and|strong="H7725"\w* \w put|strong="H4191"\w* \w it|strong="H7725"\w* \w in|strong="H4191"\w* \w that|strong="H5927"\w* \w grave|strong="H6913"\w* \w that|strong="H5927"\w* \w I|strong="H2009"\w* \w got|strong="H5927"\w* \w ready|strong="H6258"\w* \w for|strong="H4191"\w* myself.” \w And|strong="H7725"\w* \w my|strong="H7725"\w* father \w got|strong="H5927"\w* \w me|strong="H4994"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w promise|strong="H7650"\w* \w that|strong="H5927"\w* \w I|strong="H2009"\w* \w will|strong="H7725"\w* \w do|strong="H7650"\w* \w that|strong="H5927"\w*.\x * \xo 50:5 \xt Genesis 47:29-31\x* \w So|strong="H5927"\w* \w now|strong="H6258"\w*, \w please|strong="H4994"\w* \w let|strong="H4994"\w* \w me|strong="H4994"\w* \w go|strong="H5927"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w Canaan|strong="H3667"\w* country, \w so|strong="H5927"\w* \w that|strong="H5927"\w* \w I|strong="H2009"\w* \w can|strong="H4994"\w* \w bury|strong="H6912"\w* \w my|strong="H7725"\w* father \w there|strong="H8033"\w*, \w just|strong="H6258"\w* \w like|strong="H4191"\w* \w he|strong="H8033"\w* said. \w Then|strong="H2009"\w* \w I|strong="H2009"\w* \w will|strong="H7725"\w* \w come|strong="H5927"\w* \w back|strong="H7725"\w* \w here|strong="H2009"\w*.’”   
\p
